T02TD2691E:93b-1: ma h'a ma yu ri bidy'a r'a dzny'i s'u tra ta t'i k'a n'a ma /
T02TD2691E:93b-3: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i mdo'i 'bum 'grel zhes bya ba /
T02TD2691E:93b-4: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:93b-5: thub pa'i sku ni bde chen po //
T02TD2691E:93b-6: rtag tu gzhan gyi don mdzad pa //
T02TD2691E:93b-7: dpal ldan ye shes rang bzhin can //
T02TD2691E:93b-8: thub pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:93b-9: mi shes mun pa bsal ba'i phyir //
T02TD2691E:93b-10: nga yis yang dag don bsam la //
T02TD2691E:93b-12: 'di skad ces bya ba ni chos sku ste /

T02TD2691E:93b-15: de yang sku gsum gyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:93b-16: chos sku ni stong pa nyid de /
T02TD2691E:93b-17: mi dmigs pa'i ye shes so //
T02TD2691E:93b-19: de'i rang bzhin gyi grib mas me long lta bu'i ye shes te /
T02TD2691E:93b-20: sgyu ma lta bu'i sku ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o//
T02TD2691E:93b-21: de'i rang bzhin gyis stong gsum khyab pa ste /
T02TD2691E:93b-22: sprul pa'i skus sems can gyi ngon mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-24: 'di ltar ni sh'akya seng ge'i bka' ste /
T02TD2691E:93b-26: bdag gis zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:93b-27: kun rdzob kyi rang bzhin te /
T02TD2691E:93b-28: kun rdzob kyi chos de ni yang dag par log pa'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-29: log pa ni sgyu ma dang /
T02TD2691E:93b-37: de brgyad ni log pa'i kun rdzob kyi sgyu ma'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-38: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob ni don byed nus pa ste /
T02TD2691E:93b-39: 'byung ba bzhi'i rang bzhin la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-40: de'i rang bzhin ngo bo ni kun dga'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-41: thos pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:93b-42: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di thos pa'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-43: de yang mi dmigs pa'i ye shes rang bzhin med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-44: yang na sems can gyi don mdzad cing ye shes lnga shar bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:93b-45: de lta bu'i ye shes ni sus thos she na /
T02TD2691E:93b-47: dus gcig na zhes pa ni /
T02TD2691E:93b-52: lha dang mi la sogs pa tshogs pa'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:94a-2: bzhi bcom drug ldan 'khor ba mya ngan 'das /
T02TD2691E:94a-3: bzhi ni dang po 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom ste /
T02TD2691E:94a-5: gnyis pa phung po'i bdud bcom ste /
T02TD2691E:94a-7: gsum pa nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom ste ;
T02TD2691E:94a-9: bzhi pa lha'i bu'i bdud bcom ste /
T02TD2691E:94a-10: phrag dog dang ser sna bcom pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94a-11: ldan pa zhes bya ba 'di ni dpal dang mtshan nyid dang /
T02TD2691E:94a-12: gnas dang 'khor dang gdan dang yon tan dang drug go //
T02TD2691E:94a-13: yang na pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94a-14: 'das pa ni mya ngan las 'das te /

T02TD2691E:94a-16: mnyan yod na zhes bya ba ni yul ma ga dh'a yin te /

T02TD2691E:94a-19: yang dag pa'i gnas ma nor ba'o //
T02TD2691E:94a-20: mnyan yod kyi grong khyer gyi chad ni dpag tshad lnga dang ldan pa ste /

T02TD2691E:94a-26: rdzing bu de'i gzhi ni rin po che sna bdun las grub pa ste /
T02TD2691E:94a-31: pushpa r'a ga dang bdun no //
T02TD2691E:94a-32: rdzing bu de'i chu de yang dri zhim zhing tsandan gyi chu dang 'dra ste /
T02TD2691E:94a-34: dang la yang rnyog pa med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94a-35: chu de las skyes pa ni /
T02TD2691E:94a-40: ku mu ta la sogs pa me tog sna tshogs yod de /
T02TD2691E:94a-41: kha dog dkar po dkar pos mdangs phye ba /
T02TD2691E:94a-42: kha dog mthing kha mthing khas ma dangs phye ba /
T02TD2691E:94a-43: kha dog dmar po dmar pos mdangs phye ba /
T02TD2691E:94a-44: kha dog ser po ser pos mdangs phye ba /
T02TD2691E:94a-47: chu de'i nang na bya sna tshogs yod de /
T02TD2691E:94b-0: so bya rog po la sogs pas skad sna tshogs 'byin cing snyan @94b pa'o ;
T02TD2691E:94b-1: ; skyed mos tshal de la yang me tog sna tshogs yod de /
T02TD2691E:94b-4: ka ko la'i me tog dang /
T02TD2691E:94b-5: tsam pa ka'i me tog dang /
T02TD2691E:94b-7: ser po la sogs pa thang las skyes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-8: yul de'i kho ra khor yug na /
T02TD2691E:94b-17: kha rdzu ral sogs pa'i shing sna tshogs pa dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-18: shing de'i grib mas sems can thams cad bde bar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-19: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:94b-20: mnyan yod kyi rgyal po'i rgyal bu ste /
T02TD2691E:94b-21: de'i skyed mos tshal ni me tog sna tshogs yod pa /
T02TD2691E:94b-22: blta na sdug pa shin tu mtshar ba'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-24: shing sna tshogs kyis mdzes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-25: yul de'i sems can rnams 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la spyod cing tshal de la rtse ba'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-26: de bzhin du rgyal bu yang yin no //
T02TD2691E:94b-27: tshong dpon mgon med kyis bzhengs nas /
T02TD2691E:94b-28: bcom ldan 'das la sbyin par 'dod pa /
T02TD2691E:94b-29: bkra shis pa'i sa btsal te /
T02TD2691E:94b-30: gzhan nas ma rnyed pas de yang rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi skyed mos tshal na bzang do sems so //
T02TD2691E:94b-31: de nas tshong dpon mgon med kyis rgyal po la smras pa /
T02TD2691E:94b-32: ngas ni dge ba byas pa'i sa ni khyod kyi tshal bkra shis pa ngas nyo yi zhes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-34: nga'i tshal 'di ni khyod kyis nyo nus sam /
T02TD2691E:94b-35: gser gyi pha gus brtsegs nas de khengs pa'i gser 'dod de khyod kyis 'jal bar nus sam /
T02TD2691E:94b-36: de'i thog tu yang da'i ming 'jug nus sam zhes smras pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-37: de nas tshong dpon gyis gser gyi phung po byas nas gzhal te /
T02TD2691E:94b-38: rgyal po gser gyi phung po ma 'dod de /
T02TD2691E:94b-39: gser brdungs nas pa gu byas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-40: de nas tshong dpon gyis sa gzhi der gser gyi pha gus brtsegs te rgyal bu la gzhal ba'o //
T02TD2691E:94b-41: de'i steng las gzhi de ru rin po che sna bdun gyis kun dga' rab byas te /
T02TD2691E:94b-42: sgo bzhi sum thog tu byas pa /
T02TD2691E:95a-0: phyogs phyogs su ka bas rnam zas sbyin gyi ku @95a * //
T02TD2691E:95a-2: ka ba de yang rin po che sna bzhi las grub pa /

T02TD2691E:95a-4: glo skar phyi nang yang rin po che sna bdun las byas shing mu tig gi dra bas brgyan pa ste /
T02TD2691E:95a-5: phyogs gzhan yang de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:95a-6: phyogs re re la yang dpag tshad re re yod cing /
T02TD2691E:95a-7: phyi nang gnyis ka yang rin po sna bdun las byas pa'i ri mos mdzes shing blta na sdug pa'o //

T02TD2691E:95a-10: sgo re re la yang seng ge gnyis gnyis yod de /

T02TD2691E:95a-12: de bzhin du ka ba gnyis gnyis kyis mdzes shing /

T02TD2691E:95a-14: bya khyung ga ru da dang /
T02TD2691E:95a-15: ri dags sha ra na dang /

T02TD2691E:95a-17: rta babs de yang rin po che sna bdun las grub pa'o //
T02TD2691E:95a-18: kun dga' ra ba de'i thog na /

T02TD2691E:95a-29: mtshams bzhi byi ru las byas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:95a-30: de'i phyi nang yang de bzhin no //

T02TD2691E:95a-32: de bzhin du rdzing bu dang bcas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:95a-33: skyed mos tshal dang rdzing bu la yang me tog chu skyes thang skyes sna tshogs yod de /
T02TD2691E:95a-34: dri zhi ma zhing blta na sdug pa /
T02TD2691E:95a-39: sngon po la sogs pas mdzes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:95a-40: de bzhin du bya rnams kyang skad sna tshogs 'byin pas mdzes shing /
T02TD2691E:95a-41: shing ljon pa sna tshogs pa yang de bzhin no /
T02TD2691E:95a-42: tshong dpon mgon med zas sbyin zhes bya ba'i nges tig ni /
T02TD2691E:95b-0: yang na @95b dge ba'i rtsa ba thogs pa med par sbyin pas na zas sbyin zhes bya'o //
T02TD2691E:95b-1: rgyal bu'i tshal las grub pas rgyal byed tshal zhes bya'o //
T02TD2691E:95b-2: tshong dpon gyis bcom ldan 'das la phul bas mgon med zas sbyin zhes bya'o //
T02TD2691E:95b-3: de bas na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' rab na zhes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:95b-4: bzhugs te zhes bya ba ni byang chub sems dpa' dang /
T02TD2691E:95b-5: nyan thos dgra bcom pa dang /
T02TD2691E:95b-10: lha dang mi la sogs pa dang /
T02TD2691E:95b-11: thabs cig tu byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag bye ba brgyad cu rtsa bzhi thams cad kyang skye ba gcig gis thogs pa /
T02TD2691E:95b-12: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi ldog pa da bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
T02TD2691E:95b-14: rdo rje chen po rnam par thar pa dang /
T02TD2691E:95b-15: ting nge 'dzin gyis sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
T02TD2691E:95b-16: cho 'phrul chen po kun du ston pa dang /
T02TD2691E:95b-17: sems kyi skad cig thang cig yud tsam cig la sems can thams cad kyi sems dang spyod pa'i rjes su 'jug pa'i chos bstan pa /
T02TD2691E:95b-18: sna tshogs mnyam pa nyid mnyam zhing rgya che la zab pa dang /

T02TD2691E:96a-1: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byams pa la sogs pa bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang thabs cig tu bzhugs so //

T02TD2691E:96a-27: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba'i dbus su /
T02TD2691E:96a-28: rin po che rdo rje padma'i snying po seng ge'i khri la bzhugs te /
T02TD2691E:96a-29: seng ge'i khri gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:96a-30: sngon gyi smon lam gyi stobs kyis /

T02TD2691E:96a-33: rdo rje padma'i khris kun dga' rab mdzes pa dang /

T02TD2691E:96a-40: rin po che du ma'i snying po can /
T02TD2691E:96a-41: chags pa'i rin po che ke ke ru dang /
T02TD2691E:96a-42: ke ke ru chen po dang /
T02TD2691E:96a-44: aindra n'i la chen po dang /
T02TD2691E:96b-0: mdun nas 'od zer chen po bar @96b snang la khyab pas kun nas mdzes pa dang /
T02TD2691E:96b-1: rin po che rdo rje thur mas brgyan pa'i gdugs yu bas bstod pa bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag du ma'i grib mas bsgribs shing bskyabs pa /
T02TD2691E:96b-2: dpag bsam gyi shing du mas brgyan pas mdzes pa /

T02TD2691E:96b-20: de kho na thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thugs su chud /

T02TD2691E:97a-0: @97a * // bcom ldan 'das la byang chub sems dpa' dang /

T02TD2691E:97a-11: de bzhin du nyan thos dgra bcom pa rnams dang /

T02TD2691E:97a-18: lha dang lha ma yin dang mi dang mi ma yin pas mchod par 'os pa'i gnas byang chub kyi zhing khams bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyang byang chub 'grub pa'i gnas so //
T02TD2691E:97a-19: dge slong sa ri zhes bya ba ni /

T02TD2691E:107b-11: yum gyis smras pa bshums shing kha nas mi thon yang smras so //
T02TD2691E:107b-12: kye ho skyes bu dam pa nga'i bu dung gi gtsug tor can sang nyi ma phyed na nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po gser mig can gyis khyer nas za ba'i dus la bab pas thabs 'dra ba mnga' 'am zhes smras so //
T02TD2691E:107b-13: byang chub sems dpas smras pa /
T02TD2691E:107b-14: ngas rjes ni ji tsugs byed du 'ong smras so //
T02TD2691E:107b-15: de skad ces smras pa dang /
T02TD2691E:107b-16: rgya mtsho'i nang du khrid do //
T02TD2691E:107b-17: de nas klu'i rgyal po dung can gyi bu dung gi gtsug tor can lo brgyad lon pa blta na sdug pa kha dog dang ldan pa de bltas nas /
T02TD2691E:107b-19: de'i rting la byang chub sems dpa' sngar 'ong ba'i khri la dar dmar po gyon nas gzims so //
T02TD2691E:107b-20: de nas nyi ma phyed kyi dus la nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po gser mig can mchu de ni bee d'u rya dang 'dra ba mtho ba rno ba /
T02TD2691E:107b-21: mig ser zhing dmar ba la sogs pa ring zhing sngo ba /
T02TD2691E:107b-22: yan lag sder mo ring zhing rno ba /
T02TD2691E:107b-23: bya khyung gi gzugs bzhin du 'jigs pa /
T02TD2691E:107b-24: nam mkha' la 'brug sgra dang 'grogs shing /
T02TD2691E:107b-26: bar snang nas gshog pa rgya mtsho'i nang du rdebs pa /
T02TD2691E:107b-27: g-yas pa'i gshog pa brdabs pas rgya mtsho'i chu mi snang bar gyur to //
T02TD2691E:107b-28: g-yon pa brdabs pas bdun brgya'i sa'i 'og tu slebs so //
T02TD2691E:107b-29: de nas byang chub sems dpa' khri la nyal ba de tog gis blangs nas nam mkha' la khyer ro //
T02TD2691E:107b-30: de'i rting bar snang la khyer ba de byang chub sems dpa'i yab dang yum dang /
T02TD2691E:107b-31: jo mo rnams kyis mthong nas cho nges 'debs shing mya ngan las 'das so //
T02TD2691E:107b-32: de nas bya khyung des ri ma la ya'i rtse mor khyer nas sha zos khrag 'thungs te /
T02TD2691E:108a-2: byang chub sems dpas gzhogs gcig tu zlogs so //
T02TD2691E:108a-3: de nas bya khyung 'jigs pa'i sems dang ldan te /
T02TD2691E:108a-4: za ba 'phro bcad nas ngo mtshar che zhing klu rnams sngar ji tsam zos pa la 'di 'dra ba ma byung snyam nas 'phro bcad de 'dug go //
T02TD2691E:108a-5: de'i tshe byang chub dpas smras pa /
T02TD2691E:108a-6: kye rgyal po nam mkha' lding khyod kyi gsos yin mod khrag 'thung sha zo //
T02TD2691E:108a-7: de skad ces smras pa dang /
T02TD2691E:108a-8: bya khyung gis ngo mtshar che nas smras pa /
T02TD2691E:108a-9: kye khyod su yin snga ma bzhin du ma byung ngo //
T02TD2691E:108a-10: ngas kyang sngar ji tsam zos te khyod bzhin ngas ma mthong ngo ;
T02TD2691E:108a-11: ; byang chub sems dpa'i zhal nas khyod kyis 'dis ci smos zo zhig 'thungs shig ces gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:108a-12: de nas byang chub sems dpa' yab yum gyis kyang slebs nas bya khyung gi drung du cho nges 'debs shing smras so //
T02TD2691E:108a-13: kye ho nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po /
T02TD2691E:108a-14: nga'i bus nyes pa cang yod dam khyod ci nyes ci bsams zhes gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:108a-16: bya khyung de yang sdug bsngal gyis zin to //
T02TD2691E:108a-17: de nas bya khyung gis smras pa /
T02TD2691E:108a-18: kye ho byang chub sems dpa' ngas ngo ma shes na /
T02TD2691E:108a-20: das lha yul du phyin nas bdud rtsi khyer nas 'ongs nas bskus te sos par bya'o zhes gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:108a-21: de skad ces smras pa dang byang chub sems dpas smras pa /
T02TD2691E:108a-22: kye ho rgyal po khyed kyi byin gyi rlabs kyis mi byang byang chub sems dang ldan na lus sngar bzhin du song shig / de'i sems dang mi ldan na da lta bzhin du song shig ces smras so //
T02TD2691E:108a-23: de'i tshig gi bden pas lus sngar bzhin du gyur to //
T02TD2691E:108a-24: de nas byang chub sems dpas bya khyung la smras pa /
T02TD2691E:108a-25: khyod kyis rgya mtsho'i nang du song la klu rnams bos shig / ces gsungs pa dang /
T02TD2691E:108a-26: bya khyung langs nas rgya mtsho'i nang du song ngo //
T02TD2691E:108a-27: klu rnams bya khyung mthong ba dang /
T02TD2691E:108a-28: 'jigs nas da yang nga cag rnams thams cad bos te gsod snyam nas /
T02TD2691E:108a-29: de'i 'jigs pas klu rnams ma khugs /
T02TD2691E:108a-30: bya khyung yar log nas byang chub sems dpa'i drung du gnas so //
T02TD2691E:108a-31: kye byang chub sems dpa'i ngas klu rnams ma khugs so zhes so //
T02TD2691E:108b-0: byang chub @108b sems dpas smras pa /
T02TD2691E:108b-1: khyod kyis lha'i yul nas bdud rtsi khyer nas 'ongs nas khyod kyis zos pa'i keng rus kyi thog tu bdud rtsi gtor cig gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:108b-2: de nas bya khyung gis bdud rtsi gtor nas sngar shi ba'i klu rnams sos nas byung ste /
T02TD2691E:108b-3: byang chub sems dpa'i spyan sngar gnas so ;
T02TD2691E:108b-4: ; byang chub sems dpa'i zhal nas /
T02TD2691E:108b-5: bya khyung gis klu rnams ma khugs pas /
T02TD2691E:108b-6: khyed rnams kyis klu rnams bos la shog cig ces gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:108b-7: de skad ces bka' stsal pa dang /
T02TD2691E:108b-8: klu rnams kyis rgya mtsho'i nang na yod pa rnams bos nas 'ongs so //
T02TD2691E:108b-9: de'i tshe byang chub sems dpas klu rnams la sngom pa phog ste dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba'am sems can la gnod pa mi byed pa'am de sems can la gnod byed bya khyung gis 'jigs par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:108b-10: de bzhin du bya khyung gis kyang sngom pa la gnas shing /
T02TD2691E:108b-11: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo'i gzi brjid dang /
T02TD2691E:108b-12: dkon mchog gsum gyi byin rlabs kyis klu rnams la yang bya khyung gi 'jigs pa dang bral ba'o //
T02TD2691E:108b-13: de bzhin du yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pas kyang /
T02TD2691E:108b-14: klu la sogs pa'i sems can la byams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:108b-15: gad dag sa la gnas pa yi //
T02TD2691E:108b-16: 'byung po kun la nga byams so //
T02TD2691E:108b-17: zhes bya ba ni 'byung po lha dang /
T02TD2691E:108b-18: klu dang lha ma yin dang /
T02TD2691E:108b-22: mi'am ci dang lto 'phye chen po dang /
T02TD2691E:108b-33: rgyu skar la sogs pa'i gdon rnams yin te /
T02TD2691E:108b-34: 'byung po de rnams kyang stong phrag brgyad cu brgyad cu gnas te /
T02TD2691E:108b-35: de dag sa la rgyu ba rnams yin te /
T02TD2691E:108b-36: de bzhin du nam mkha' dang /
T02TD2691E:108b-38: de kun la yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis byams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:108b-39: sems can gang dag gnas par bcas //
T02TD2691E:108b-40: sems can kun la nga byams so //
T02TD2691E:108b-41: zhes bya ba ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams nas gzhan yang 'jig rten gyi khams la yang de bzhin te /
T02TD2691E:108b-42: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid dang /
T02TD2691E:109a-0: @109a * // rdul phra mo la gnas pa'i sems can rnams la yang byams so //
T02TD2691E:109a-1: sems can kun dang srog chags kun //
T02TD2691E:109a-2: 'byung po dag ni thams cad kyang //
T02TD2691E:109a-3: zhes bya ba ni bden pa'i tshig 'dis dug gi nad bsam pa dang /
T02TD2691E:109a-7: bsdad pa'i dug ni rtsa ba dang lo ma la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-8: byed pa'i dug ni sbyor ba las byung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-9: dug de dag thams cad kyang sems can dang srog chags dang 'byung po rnams la yang byams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-10: thams cad bde ba 'ba' zhig shog / thams cad nad ni med gyur cig / ces bya ba ni 'jig rten gyi sdug bsngal brgyad dang /
T02TD2691E:109a-12: mkhris pa dang bad kan las gyur pa de la sogs pa nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi rnams yin te /
T02TD2691E:109a-13: bden pa'i tshig des de rnams kyi sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral zhing bde bar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-14: kun du bzang po mthong bar shog / gang yang sdig par ma gyur cig / ces bya ba ni mnar med pa'i sems can nas tshangs pa'i yul man chad kyi bde bar gnas /
T02TD2691E:109a-17: bag chags kyi sgrib pa dang bral ba'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-18: yang na shes nas byas pa dang mi shes nas byas pa rnams dang yang bral ba'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-19: byams pa'i sems la gnas nas su //
T02TD2691E:109a-20: dug ni rab tu gsad par bya //
T02TD2691E:109a-21: zhes bya ba ni byams pa ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten la gnas pa'i sems can la bu gcig po lam byams pa lta bu ste /
T02TD2691E:109a-22: de nye bar gzhag pa'i sems kyis snying rje 'ba' zhig tu 'khor ba la gnas pa'i sems can la snying rje ba'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-23: des sems can thon pa'i sems kyis des rab tu dga' ba'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-24: de mnyam pa nyid du gzhag pas btang snyoms so //
T02TD2691E:109a-25: 'dir ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pas /
T02TD2691E:109a-26: dge slong sa ri'i don la sems can thams cad kyi don gyis nang gi dug gsum dang phyi'i dug gsum zad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109a-27: nang gi dug gsum ni 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum mo //
T02TD2691E:109a-28: phyi'i dug gsum ni de nye bar gzhag pas byung ba /
T02TD2691E:109b-0: 'gro ba dang bsdad pa @109b dang byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-1: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid dang /
T02TD2691E:109b-2: sangs rgyas kyi bden pas byams pas dug zad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-3: bsrung dang yongs su bzung ba dang //
T02TD2691E:109b-4: de bzhin yongs su bskyang bar bya //
T02TD2691E:109b-5: zhes bya ba ni tshigs su bcad pa'i bden pa 'dis te /
T02TD2691E:109b-6: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi bka'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-7: de yang 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnam gzigs dang //
T02TD2691E:109b-8: gtsug tor can dang kun skyob dang /
T02TD2691E:109b-9: log dang sel dang gser thub 'od srungs so //
T02TD2691E:109b-10: de la sogs pa'i 'das pa'i sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed rnams kyis gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-11: ma 'ongs pa ni de bzhin du byams pa la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-12: da ltar ba ni sh'akya seng ge ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-13: dge slong sa ri'i don la sems can rnams la gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-14: de bzhin de dang de 'dra'i srung ba dam ba ni /
T02TD2691E:109b-15: srung ba dam pa sba ba dang yongs su bskyab pa dang /
T02TD2691E:109b-19: 'di'i rig pa gang 'dzin pas srung zhing yongs su bskyang bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:109b-20: sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal byang chub phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:109b-21: zhes bya ba ni ngo bo nyid dang bral zhing dmigs pa med pa ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-22: 'das pa dang srid pa'i ngo bo med cing da ltar byung ba yang med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-23: de'i sgrib pas sgyu ma lta bu ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-24: me long gi lto ba'i grib ma lta bu ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-25: de ni gzugs sku dang po ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-26: de nye bar gzhag pa'i ngo bos stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams sprul pa'i skus khyab ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-27: de yang gzugs sku gnyis pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-28: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan zhing dpe byad brgyad cus sku la brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:109b-29: sems can gyi don byed pa ni thub pa'i sku'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-30: de lta bu'i sku gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:109b-31: byang chub ni tshad med pa bzhi'i sgo nas sems can rnams la byams pa ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-32: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu'i tshogs kyi lam ste /
T02TD2691E:109b-34: ; de la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni /
T02TD2691E:109b-35: byams pa dang 'jam dpal la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-36: de rnams la phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:109b-37: grol gyur phyag 'tshal grol la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:109b-38: zhes bya ba ni bag chags dang shes bya'i sgrib pas ma gos pa ste /
T02TD2691E:110a-1: ye shes rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:110a-2: de'i ngo bo ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-3: de lta bu la phyag 'tshal zhes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-4: zhi gyur phyag 'tshal zhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:110a-5: zhes bya ba ni zhi ni lam yin te /
T02TD2691E:110a-7: pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi lam nas sangs rgyas pa dang /
T02TD2691E:110a-8: smon lam gyi stobs kyis sems can gyi don byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-9: de bas na zhi gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:110a-10: 'bras bu yin te 'gyur ba med pa rang bzhin dang bral bas /
T02TD2691E:110a-11: ye shes rnam par gsal ba ste /
T02TD2691E:110a-12: ye shes de yang dmigs pa med pa'i rang bzhin gyi 'bras bu'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-13: gzhi la mi gnas pa'i phyir zhi 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:110a-14: gzhi dang gzhi la mi gnas pas phyag 'tshal zhes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-15: rnam grol phyag 'tshal grol la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:110a-17: 'khor ba las grol bas na grol ba ste /
T02TD2691E:110a-18: 'khor ba ni ma rig pa dang 'du byed dang rnam par shes pa dang ming dang gzugs dang skye mched drug dang /
T02TD2691E:110a-25: rga shi dang bcu gnyis so //
T02TD2691E:110a-26: 'du byed la sogs pa bkag pa'i phyir na /
T02TD2691E:110a-28: de grol na ma rig pa'i ming yang ci smos te /
T02TD2691E:110a-29: de bas na rnam par grol la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:110a-30: bram ze gang dag sdig pa'i chos rnams bsal bar gyur pa de dag la yang phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:110a-31: tshangs par spyod cing dgra bcom pa'i rang bzhin yin te /
T02TD2691E:110a-32: de yang zag pa zad cing bag chags kyi dri mas mi bsgo ba'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-33: de nas bram ze'i sdig pas mi bsgo ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2691E:110a-34: yang na bram ze'i tshul du gnas pas bram ze'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-35: de dag gis bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:110a-36: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo'i gzi brjid dang bden pa'i tshig gis gang zag sems can thams cad dang kun bde bar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-37: 'jigs pa thams cad dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:110a-38: 'jig rten phyi'i ngan song gsum gyi 'jigs pa dang /
T02TD2691E:110a-39: rkyen las byung ba'i nga ltar byung ba'i 'jigs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110a-40: tshe phyi ma'i ngan song 'byung ba ni dang po dmyal ba yin te /
T02TD2691E:110a-41: tsha ba'i dmyal ba la brgyad do //
T02TD2691E:110b-7: mnar med pa dang brgyad do //
T02TD2691E:110b-8: yang grang ba la chu bur can dang /
T02TD2691E:110b-9: chu bur can chen po dang /
T02TD2691E:110b-13: autpa la ltar gas pa dang /
T02TD2691E:110b-15: padma chen po ltar gyes pa dang brgyad do //
T02TD2691E:110b-16: dmyal ba de rnams kyi 'khor ni re re la yang bcu drug bcu drug go //
T02TD2691E:110b-17: de'i ming ni mtshon gyi sen mo dang /
T02TD2691E:110b-32: sla ngas brngo ba dang bcu drug go //
T02TD2691E:110b-33: de ni tshe phyi ma'i dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal dang 'jigs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110b-34: yang gnyis pa dud 'gro'i 'jigs pa ni gang gis gang za ba'i 'jigs pa ste /
T02TD2691E:110b-35: srog dang 'bral ba'i rang bzhin gyis dud 'gro'i sdug bsngal ni shin tu 'jigs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110b-36: gsum pa yi dags kyi 'jigs pa ni /
T02TD2691E:110b-37: 'thung ba dang za ba med cing gang gis yang mthong ba la yang phrag dog gis 'thab rtsod byed cing /
T02TD2691E:110b-38: yi dags kyi sdug bsngal de rnams so //
T02TD2691E:110b-39: da ltar rkyan gyis 'jigs pa ni /
T02TD2691E:110b-40: 'byung po'i gdon ma rungs pa'i 'jigs pa dang /
T02TD2691E:110b-41: gzhan dgra bo dang phrad pa dang /
T02TD2691E:110b-42: de la sogs pa'i 'jigs pa brgyad dang de la 'jigs pas na 'jigs pa dang zhes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110b-43: gnod pa thams cad dang zhes bya ba ni dge ba'i rtsa ba la gnod pa ste /
T02TD2691E:110b-44: bdud bzhi'i rang bzhin gyis bgegs kyi tshul du byas nas mi dang mi ma yin pas gnod pa skyel ba'o //
T02TD2691E:110b-45: nad 'go ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:110b-50: de rnams ni yud tsam la 'gos pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110b-51: yang na 'brum bu'i nad dang gzhan gyis mi thub cing /
T02TD2691E:110b-52: sdig pa'i nang du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:110b-53: 'khrug pa thams cad dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:110b-54: gzhan gyi dpung gis 'dren pa dang /
T02TD2691E:110b-55: rang yul du khrag khrug 'byung ba dang /
T02TD2691E:111a-2: rims thams cad dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:111a-3: bad kan dang mkhris pa dang /
T02TD2691E:111a-4: rlung las gyur pa de ni 'dus pa ste /
T02TD2691E:111a-5: gnyis gnyis 'grogs pa ni ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:111a-6: nad de dang ldan pas na rims so //
T02TD2691E:111a-7: nad thams cad dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:111a-15: lkog ma'i lha gor na ba dang /
T02TD2691E:111a-19: rtsi ba logs na ba dang /
T02TD2691E:111a-25: rab tu skye gnas na ba dang /
T02TD2691E:111a-32: nying lag na ba la sogs pa nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'o //
T02TD2691E:111a-33: gdon thams cad dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:111a-34: lha'i gdon la sogs pa bgegs rigs mi gcig pa stong phrag brgyad cu phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
T02TD2691E:111a-35: dug thams cad las srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:111a-36: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid dang sangs rgyas kyi bden pa'i tshig gis 'gro ba dang /
T02TD2691E:111a-37: bsdad pa dang byed pa'i dug bcom /
T02TD2691E:111a-38: sems can thams cad bde bar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:111a-39: lo brgya 'tsho bar gyur cig / ston brgya mthong bar shog shig / ces bya ba ni 'di 'chang ba dang /
T02TD2691E:111a-41: tshe ring zhing bkra shis te /
T02TD2691E:111a-42: sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral ba'o //
T02TD2691E:111a-43: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i bden pa'i tshig gi gnas skabs te bzhi pa'o /
T02TD2691E:111a-45: // / kun dga' bo sngon byung ba ri'i rgyal po gangs ri'i lho phyogs kyi ngos la /
T02TD2691E:111a-46: rma bya'i rgyal mo gser du snang ba zhes bya ba cig gnas te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:111a-47: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gtsug tor can gyi bstan pa la /

T02TD2691E:111b-9: smad pa la sogs pa'i rims thams cad kyis mi tshugs shing /
T02TD2691E:111b-10: dran pa tsam gyis sos par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:111b-11: gangs kyi ri ni lho'i 'dzam bu'i gling gi rdo rje'i gdan gyi byang phyogs na /

T02TD2691E:111b-19: de bzhin du bskor nas lho dang nub dang byang phyogs la yang yin no //
T02TD2691E:111b-20: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo gser du snang ba yang /
T02TD2691E:111b-21: sems can gyi don la gangs kyi ri la gnas shing /
T02TD2691E:111b-22: lha dang lha ma yin dang /
T02TD2691E:111b-24: klu dang mi ma yin la sogs pas mchod cing rma bya'i gzugs su snang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:111b-25: bzhin ni 'dzam bu'i gling gi gser gyi mdog 'dra ba /
T02TD2691E:111b-26: de'i lus la mchu bee d'uryas byas pa /
T02TD2691E:111b-27: gshog pa dang mjug ma ni rin po che sna bdun gyis byas pa /
T02TD2691E:111b-28: rin po che sna bdun gyis byas pa'i khri la bsdad cing /
T02TD2691E:111b-29: dug gi me tog gis brgyan cing dug za ba'o //
T02TD2691E:111b-30: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo 'di ni /
T02TD2691E:111b-33: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis rjes su yi rang zhing byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:111b-34: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du gnas pas rma bya ste /
T02TD2691E:111b-35: yang na rma bya'i phyag rgyas /
T02TD2691E:111b-36: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
T02TD2691E:111b-37: rang sangs rgyas dang nyan thos dang sems can thams cad la rig sngags kyi phyag rgyas btab pas na rma bya'o //
T02TD2691E:111b-38: chen mo ni bsam gyis mi khyab ba'o //
T02TD2691E:111b-39: gser du snang ba ni gser bzhin du dkon pa ste /

T02TD2691E:112a-28: mtshon byed ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'o //

T02TD2691E:112a-35: rgyab dregs tshul dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:112a-36: g-yas dkar g-yon dmar rgyab ljang gu'o //
T02TD2691E:112a-37: rgyan thams cad dang sbrul gyis brgyan cing /

T02TD2691E:112a-39: phyag g-yas pa rnams na ral gri dang /
T02TD2691E:112a-43: phyag g-yon pa rnams na sdigs mdzub dang /
T02TD2691E:112b-4: phung po ni rnam par shes pa'i phung po yin /
T02TD2691E:112b-5: khams ni nam mkha'i khams so //
T02TD2691E:112b-6: skye mched ni yid kyi skye mched do //
T02TD2691E:112b-7: padma sna tshogs kyi steng du nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs shing /
T02TD2691E:112b-8: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i 'od dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:112b-9: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yi ge h'um /
T02TD2691E:112b-11: de yang rig sngags kyi snying gar bsam mo //
T02TD2691E:112b-12: sems can gyi don gyis rin po che rdo rje'i rigs kyi snying po'o //

T02TD2691E:112b-15: klu dang 'byung po rnams 'pho bar 'dod na /
T02TD2691E:112b-16: 'bum phrag khri bzlas pa byas nas gu gul dang btsan dug gi du ba btang zhing yungs kar gyis gdug pa can gyi gnas la brdeg / rin po che rdo rje'i rigs kyi rig sngags su bsams la /
T02TD2691E:112b-17: gdug pa can rnams brlag par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:112b-19: dug dang gu gul nag po bsres nas na sar bdug par bya ste /
T02TD2691E:112b-20: byug pa'i sman ni btsan dug nag po dang /
T02TD2691E:112b-27: mi'i zhun gyis sbyar la byug pa bya'o //
T02TD2691E:112b-28: sngags kyis brdegs 'dod na yungs kar dang rma bya'i sgros brdeg go //
T02TD2691E:112b-29: dug zos na chu la gdab po //
T02TD2691E:112b-30: rig sngags kya rgyal mo rma bya chen mo klu'i srog snying ni gang zhe na /

T02TD2691E:113a-11: 'byung po rnams kyis kyang mi tshugs so //
T02TD2691E:113a-12: rgyags pas myos nas rab tu rmongs shing brgyal ba dang zhes bya ba ni /

T02TD2691E:113a-22: bya'i rgyal po rma bya'i gzugs su snang ste /
T02TD2691E:113a-23: rma bya'i nang nas gang la gang gi gzugs ston te /
T02TD2691E:113a-24: sems can de dag gi gzugs su byas nas 'dul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:113a-25: sems can bya'i gzugs su byas shing 'dul ba ste /
T02TD2691E:113a-26: de dag gi gzugs kyis sems can 'dul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:113a-27: sems can lha'i gzugs su byas nas /
T02TD2691E:113a-28: de dag gi gzugs kyis sems can 'dul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:113a-29: sems can 'byung po'i gzugs su byas nas /

T02TD2691E:113a-31: kun dga'i ra ba nas kun dga'i ra ba'i bar /
T02TD2691E:113a-32: skyed mos tshal nas skyed mos tshal du /

T02TD2691E:113a-34: de'i dbus su rma bya gser gyi mdog can blta na sdug pa ;

T02TD2691E:113b-29: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya ba ni /

T02TD2691E:114b-38: da ltar mi gnas pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:114b-39: chos la phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:115a-1: mi gnas rgya cher khyab pa /
T02TD2691E:115a-2: rtog pa'i rang bzhin sems nyid la'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-3: dge 'dun la phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:115a-4: dge ba mang po de 'dus pa des sdig pa bshags pa ste /
T02TD2691E:115a-5: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa dag pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-6: rma bya'i rgyal mo gser du snang ba la phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya ba ni ;
T02TD2691E:115a-7: rma ni sgyu ma lta bu'i rang bzhin chos thams cad mi dmigs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-8: bya ni ye shes kyi rang bzhin ma rig mun pa rang bsal gnyug ma'i rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:115a-9: 'di ni gnas med cing gang gis mi 'grub mi skye ba med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-10: yang na rma bya ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
T02TD2691E:115a-11: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi yum mo //
T02TD2691E:115a-12: gser du snang ba ni gser bzhin du kha dog gsal zhing blta na sdug pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-13: rgyal mo ni bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-14: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:115a-15: rig pa ni stong pa nyid do //
T02TD2691E:115a-16: stong pa nyid ni shes rab bo//
T02TD2691E:115a-17: shes rab ni mi dmigs pa'i rang bzhin /
T02TD2691E:115a-18: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i ye shes so //
T02TD2691E:115a-19: sngags ni ma manda'i don gyis bskyab pa dang /
T02TD2691E:115a-20: skyob pa'i rang bzhin stong pa nyid du gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-21: rgyal mo ni ma rig pa las rgyal ba ste ma rig pa de ni 'khor ba'i rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-22: 'khor ba'i rgyu de ni bdud bzhi'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-23: de las rgyal bsan [*bas na?] rgyal mo'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-24: chen mo ni bsam gyis mi khyab cing nam mkha' bzhin du 'jig rten gyi khams rnams la khyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-25: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags kyi tshig gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:115a-27: siddhe su siddhe la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-28: sangs rgyas thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:115a-29: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo phyag rgyas btab pa /
T02TD2691E:115a-32: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas rnams so //
T02TD2691E:115a-34: bsrung ba mdzad du gsol zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:115a-35: gang zag sems can thams cad dang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mos bsrung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-36: lo brgya 'tsho bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:115a-37: 'di la 'chang pa dang gus par byed pa tshe ring zhing bkra shis te /
T02TD2691E:115a-38: nad thams cad dang bral ba'o //
T02TD2691E:115a-39: ston brgya mthong bar shog cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:115a-40: ji srid ma shi'i bar du bde bar gnas shing yang nas yang du tshe bsnan par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:115b-0: rig sngags kyi rgyal @115b mo 'di kun gzhi rnam par dag pas thabs shes rab gnyis su med spa mtshon par bye de pa ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes te /
T02TD2691E:115b-1: mtshon byed ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo'o //
T02TD2691E:115b-2: rigs ni rin po che dang padma'i rigs so //
T02TD2691E:115b-3: 'du shes kyi phung po me'i khams lce'i skye mched do //
T02TD2691E:115b-4: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gsal zhing /
T02TD2691E:115b-5: phyag brgyad sku mdog dmar mo'o //
T02TD2691E:115b-6: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2691E:115b-8: spyan gsum pa rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:115b-9: zhal dang po cung zad khro ba /
T02TD2691E:115b-10: g-yas zhi ba g-yon dregs tshul dang ldan pa /
T02TD2691E:115b-13: g-yon mthing ga / rgyab ljang gu'o //
T02TD2691E:115b-16: padma'i steng du zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:115b-17: phyag g-yas pa rnams na ral gri dang /
T02TD2691E:115b-27: sems can thams cad la thugs rje'i spyan gyis gzigs pa'i rig sngags kyi gsang sngags 'dis char 'bebs pa'i thabs ni rig sngags kyi gzhung du byas nas /
T02TD2691E:115b-29: sngags 'di bris nas mnan par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:115b-30: de bzhin du klu gang gnas pa'i ming byang bris la /
T02TD2691E:115b-34: mi zhun bsres la sdong bu byas te /
T02TD2691E:115b-35: de mnan pa dang bsreg par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:115b-36: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni 'di yin te /
T02TD2691E:115b-38: klu mtha' yas la sos pa bskul bar bya'o //
T02TD2691E:115b-44: de bzhin du byas na the tshom med cing /
T02TD2691E:115b-46: rin chen rigs kyi padma'i rig sngags 'dis dug za bar gyur na /
T02TD2691E:115b-47: zas la btab la spyin no //
T02TD2691E:115b-48: 'byung po rnams byung na snying ga la btab po //
T02TD2691E:115b-49: rims nad byung na spyi bo'i gtsug tu sngar shad pa'i sman dang sngags gdab bo //
T02TD2691E:115b-50: de ltar byas na the tshom med do //
T02TD2691E:116a-1: pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi bka'o //
T02TD2691E:116a-2: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:116a-3: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pas sems can gyi don la kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
T02TD2691E:116a-4: de'i tshe de'i dus na zhes bya ba ni sngon mi de'i dus na rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo byung ba'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:116a-5: rma bya'i rgyal mo gser du snang ba zhes bya ba de zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:116a-8: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsung zhing /
T02TD2691E:116a-9: rjes su yi rang ba sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral bar byed pa /
T02TD2691E:116a-10: phyi'i dug dang nang gi dug 'joms pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116a-11: gzhan yin pa snyam du khyod sems na /
T02TD2691E:116a-12: de ltar mi lta'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:116a-13: sngon yang gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma stong phrag brgyad khri brgyad cu rnams de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs te /
T02TD2691E:116a-14: de ltar yang ngas gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116a-15: de bzhin du ma 'ongs pa rnams kyis kyang gsung bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:116a-16: de ci'i phyir zhe na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:116a-17: rig sngags kyi rang bzhin bsam gyis mi khyab pa brjod du med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116a-18: rig sngags kyi rang bzhin slob dpon las kyi rdo rjes tshigs su bcad de gsungs pa /
T02TD2691E:116a-19: sems ni sems kyis rig ma yin /
T02TD2691E:116a-20: ji srid sgro btags thams cad ni //
T02TD2691E:116a-21: de kun thams cad med pas na //
T02TD2691E:116a-22: rig pa'i don la sgro btags med //
T02TD2691E:116a-23: des ni dgag dang sgrub ba med //
T02TD2691E:116a-24: shes pa gang zhig lhun grub pa /
T02TD2691E:116a-25: de la bsam gyis mi khyab brjod //
T02TD2691E:116a-26: bsam bzhin du ni mi khyab pa //
T02TD2691E:116a-27: de la bsam gyis mi khyab brjod //
T02TD2691E:116a-28: gang zhig 'gro ba ma skyes zhes //
T02TD2691E:116a-29: blo ni rtag pa rtog pa nyid ;
T02TD2691E:116a-30: ;'gro ba'i gnyug ma bde ba nyid //
T02TD2691E:116a-31: blo dang ldan bas 'bad pa med //
T02TD2691E:116a-32: sgro btags kun las nges grol ba //
T02TD2691E:116a-33: bdag gi de nyid du ni brjod //
T02TD2691E:116a-34: stong pa la sogs mngon brjod pa //
T02TD2691E:116a-35: de la sgro btags brjod pa yis //
T02TD2691E:116a-37: dbu ma'i lam nas rig pa'i don bstan ba'o //
T02TD2691E:116a-38: de bas na kun dga' bo zhes brjod pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116a-39: da [*nga?] nyid de'i che de'i dus na rma bya'i rgyal mo gser du snang ba zhes bya bar gyur to zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:116a-40: de'i ngo bo nyid rig pa'i rgyal mor snang ste /
T02TD2691E:116a-41: de ni kun rdzob kyi rang bzhin gyis sems can gyi don la snang bar gyur pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-0: @116b kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni sems can gyi don la bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-1: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i snying po 'di yang dag par bzlas par bya'o zhes bya ba ni sems can gyi don gyi glags pa de nyid yin te /
T02TD2691E:116b-2: stong pa nyid kyis ma grub pas /
T02TD2691E:116b-3: ma mantra'i don du skyabs dang skyob pa'i don gyis rin chen rigs kyi las kyi sprul pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-4: de yang kun gzhi rnam par dag pa ni stong pa nyid yin te /
T02TD2691E:116b-5: thabs dang shes rab bral ba'i ye shes ni 'ching ba'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-6: shes rab dang thabs dang 'dzom pa'i ye shes ni grol ba'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-7: sus gsungs she na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
T02TD2691E:116b-8: 'phags pa dri ma med par bstan pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo nas kyang gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:116b-9: shes rab bral ba'i thabs kyang 'ching do //
T02TD2691E:116b-10: thabs dang bral ba'i shes rab kyang 'ching ba'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-11: shes rab dang bcas pa'i thabs ni thar pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-12: thabs dang bcas pa'i shes rab ni thar pa'o zhes gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:116b-13: 'di dag de'i bdag nyid ni bla ma'i man ngag nyid nas sgron ma dang snang ba bzhin du lhan cig skyes pa ltar bsgrub pa bzhin du rtogs par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-14: de bas na stong pa nyid dang snying rje dbyer med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-15: 'dir yang stong pa nyid ni ye shes te mtshon par byed pa de bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes so //
T02TD2691E:116b-16: bdag nyid lta bu'i mtshon byed ni rin chen las kyi rigs kyi rma bya chen mo'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-21: btang snyoms kyi sgo nas rnam par dag pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-22: sku mdag ljang gur bstan pa ni /
T02TD2691E:116b-23: rig sngags 'dis las thams cad 'grub par bstan ba'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-28: dmar po'i zhal ni zhi ba la sogs pa'i las rnam bzhi bstan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-29: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga'i dbu rgyan can ni /
T02TD2691E:116b-30: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin bstan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:116b-31: dbu la sna tshogs kyi rdo rjes brgyan pa ni /
T02TD2691E:116b-32: rigs ma nges pa las kyi rigs kyi mtshan nyid do //
T02TD2691E:116b-34: ting nge 'dzin nye bar bstan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-0: khro mor sgom pa ni theg pa sna tshogs yod pas theg pa chen po'i rang bzhin @117a * //
T02TD2691E:117a-2: sbrul gyis yan lag brgyan pa ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-3: ma rungs pa'i gdug pa can klu dang gnod sbyin la sogs pa 'dul ba'i phyir ro //
T02TD2691E:117a-4: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-5: pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi rnam par dag pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-6: phyag brgyad du bstan pa ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-7: rnam par thar pa brgyad do //
T02TD2691E:117a-8: g-yas dang po na ral gri bsnams pa ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-9: shes rab kyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:117a-10: de'i 'og ma na rdo rje 'dzin pa ni ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin thabs so //
T02TD2691E:117a-11: g-yon dang po sdigs mdzub zhags pa ni 'gro ba ma lus pa'i sems can thams cad bcings pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-12: de'i 'og ma rtse gsum 'dzin pa ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-13: nges par srid pa gsum 'joms pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-14: bar ma g-yas g-yon gnyis na mda' gzhu 'gengs pa ni thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i brda bstan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-15: 'og ma g-yas g-yon gnyis na rma bya'i sgro bsnams pa ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-16: nang gi dug dang phyi'i dug nges par 'joms pa'o//
T02TD2691E:117a-17: zhabs g-yas brkyang pas klu mnan pa ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-19: g-yon bskum pas gnod sbyin mya ngan gyi tshul gyis mnan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-20: padma sna tshogs kyi gdan ni theg pa sna tshogs bstan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-21: nyi zla gdan la bting ba ni thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-22: 'od zer sna tshogs dang ldan pa ni khro bo'i tshul gyis gdug pa can rnams 'dul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-23: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin ni rigs lnga rnam par dag pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-24: rin chen rigs kyi rma bya chen mo ni /
T02TD2691E:117a-25: las thams cad grub cing dug thams cad bcom pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-27: rig sngags bzlas shing gdong bzlog ste /
T02TD2691E:117a-28: rig sngags kyi rang bzhin byas nas g-yas na zor ba 'dzin pa g-yon na zhags pa 'dzin pa /
T02TD2691E:117a-29: rig sngags bzlas shing drag bor gdong bzlog par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:117a-31: gro ba 'am shing shun nam ras la bris la /
T02TD2691E:117a-32: mgul lam lag pa g-yas pa la gdags so //
T02TD2691E:117a-33: nad pa gso bar 'dod na rig sngags kyi snying po 'di bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-1: mi'i zhun gyis sbyar bar bya'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-4: des byas na nad rnams med par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:117b-5: dug 'thungs na chu la btab la sbyin no //
T02TD2691E:117b-6: las thams cad grub pa'i rig sngags kyi gsang sngags gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:117b-8: ai ti mi ti la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-9: yang las kyi rdo rjes tshigs su bcad de gsungs pa /
T02TD2691E:117b-10: gang zhig gang zag 'di grub na //
T02TD2691E:117b-13: dri ma thams cad 'dis bral lo //
T02TD2691E:117b-14: skad cig mas ni bsgom byas na //
T02TD2691E:117b-16: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams gsungs pa //
T02TD2691E:117b-17: gnyis pa'i sems ni 'dir med do //
T02TD2691E:117b-19: kun dga' po zhes bya ba ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhal nas sems can don du bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-20: 'di ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i snying po yin no zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:117b-21: bsrung ba'i dam pa las kyi snying po gang du yang dran par gyur na grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:117b-22: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:117b-23: yang nas yang du sangs rgyas kyis 'gro ba rigs drug gi don du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-24: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di grong na 'dug na yang yid la bya'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:117b-25: yid bzhin gyi nor bu 'di 'dug par gyur nas rjes su yi rang nas /
T02TD2691E:117b-26: rmi lam ngan pa dang ltas ngan pa bzlog par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:117b-27: dgon pa na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni bsgom pa la bar chod med cing myur du bsgom pa 'grub pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-28: lam na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni 'gro ba'i bsam pa grub cing /
T02TD2691E:117b-29: myur du bkra shis par sleb pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-30: lam gol ba na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni 'gro ba'i dus su dgra dang mi phrad cing 'gro ba'i bsam pa grub cing /
T02TD2691E:117b-31: myur du khyim du sleb pa'o //
T02TD2691E:117b-32: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:117b-33: rgyal pos chad pas mi gcod cing byams pa'i gtam thob par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:117b-34: chom rkun gyi nang na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:117b-35: de rnams kyis mi mthong zhing rang gi yul du nye bar sleb ste /
T02TD2691E:117b-36: gal te mthong bar gyur na rig sngags kyi gzi brjid kyis 'joms par mi 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118a-2: khyim mam yul lam nags tshal mes tshig par gyur na /
T02TD2691E:118a-3: de'i nang du chud nas kyang me'i 'jigs pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118a-4: chu'i nang na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-5: rgya mtsho'i nang na rdzing chen po las rgal ba 'am /
T02TD2691E:118a-7: rab rgal la sogs pa'i chu'i nang du chud pas kyang /
T02TD2691E:118a-8: chu de rnams kyi 'jigs pa med cing /
T02TD2691E:118a-9: bkra shis pas rang gi khyim du sleb bo //
T02TD2691E:118a-10: dgra'i nang na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-11: gzhan yang glags tshol zhing dgra bor gyur pa'am /
T02TD2691E:118a-12: do mi shes shing dgra'i yul du song ba la /
T02TD2691E:118a-13: rig sngags dran pa tsam gyis dgra bo'i nang nas yang thar bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118a-14: phyir rgol ba dang dgra bo'i nang na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-15: skungs kyi nang du chud pa'am /
T02TD2691E:118a-17: 'di yid la byas pas na de rnams kyi nang du chud na yang grol bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118a-18: 'khor gyi nang na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-19: 'khor de yang ngan sems skyed par 'gyur pas na /
T02TD2691E:118a-20: de'i sems de bzlog par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118a-21: de bas na rig pa de yang yid la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:118a-22: rtsod pa'i nang na 'dug gam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-23: rtsod pa la yang gnyis te /
T02TD2691E:118a-24: phyi rig pa la sbos pas rtsod pa dang /
T02TD2691E:118a-25: nor gyi khyim la mi mthun pas rtsod pa'o //
T02TD2691E:118a-26: de la yid la byed par gyur na yang rgyal bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118a-27: sbrul gyis zin tam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-28: gdug pa can rnams 'chi ba'i dug gis zin pa rig sngags kyi rgyal mo 'di yid la dran pa tsam gyis kyang dug des kyang mi tshugs par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118a-29: dug 'thungs sam zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-30: sbyor ba'i dug dang bsdad pa'i dug 'thung bar gyur pa rnams kyang rig sngags kyi snying po 'di tshar bdun nam /
T02TD2691E:118a-31: lan grangs nyi shu rtsa gcig gam brgya rtsa brgyad dam de chu la btab nas 'thungs na yang mi tshugs so //
T02TD2691E:118a-32: 'jigs pa thams cad 'dus pa na yang yid la bya'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118a-33: gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i rig sngags kyi snying po ni yid bzhin gyi nor bu bzhin du shin tu dkon pa 'di yid la byas par gyur na /
T02TD2691E:118a-34: dus ma yin pa'i 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa chen po brgyad las kyang thar bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118b-0: gzhan yang 'jigs pa @118b phra mo las thar bar 'gyur te /
T02TD2691E:118b-1: rlung las gyur pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-2: rlung gi nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi yang rig sngags kyi gzi brjid kyis zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118b-3: mkhris pa las gyur pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-4: de bzhin du mkhris pa'i nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi las kyang thar bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118b-5: bad kan las gyur pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-6: bad kan kyang bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi yin te /
T02TD2691E:118b-7: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid dang yid la byas par gyur na de rnams kyis kyang mi tshugs so //
T02TD2691E:118b-8: 'dus pa las gyur pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-11: de gsum 'dus pas na 'dus pa zhes bya ste//
T02TD2691E:118b-12: ldan pa ni gang dag gnyis ldan pas na ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:118b-13: de lta bu'i nad la yang yid la byed par gyur na /
T02TD2691E:118b-14: nad de kun gyis kyang mi tshugs so //
T02TD2691E:118b-15: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi las nad gang yang rung bas btab par gyur pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-16: gzhan mi gcig pa re re la yang mi gcig pa bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi gnas te /
T02TD2691E:118b-17: nad de rnams kyis kyang mi tshugs so //
T02TD2691E:118b-18: phongs par gyur na yang shin tu yid la bya'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-19: phongs pa la rnam pa gsum ste /
T02TD2691E:118b-23: de kun gyis phongs na yang rig sngags 'di yid la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:118b-25: kun dga' bo la smras pa'o //
T02TD2691E:118b-26: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-27: bcom ldan 'das kyis kun dga' bo la lan du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:118b-28: gsad pa'i rigs pa ni chad pas bral bar 'gyur zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-29: rgyal po'am gzhan yang 'byung po la sogs pas gsad pa'i sems yod pa la de rnams kyis kyang mi tshugs par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118b-30: chad pas gcad pa'i rigs pa ni gzhu btsog gis so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-31: sems ngan zhing chad pa gcod 'dod pa'i sems de la yang byams pa'i sems dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:118b-32: gzhu btsog gi rigs pa ni brgyad pas so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:118b-33: gzhu btsog cing skur pa gdab 'dod pa de yang bkag cing snying rje'i sems dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:118b-34: brgyad bkag pa'i rigs pa ni dam bcas pas so //
T02TD2691E:118b-35: brgyad de byed par 'dod pa'i sems dang ldan par byed pa yang brgya khrol zhing mi snang bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-1: pa'i rigs pa ni spu zing zhes bya bas so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-7: spu zing zhes bya ba'i rigs pa ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-8: de bzhin du thar par 'gyur te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-9: dug lnga'i rang bzhin gyis bkag pa'i mun pa ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-10: rang bsal ye shes kyis snang bar 'gyur ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-12: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i rig pas snang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-13: de'i nad thams cad kyang ldog par 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-14: ma rig pa'i mun pas bkag nas /
T02TD2691E:119a-15: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi nad yin te /
T02TD2691E:119a-16: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i gzi brjid kyis me mar gyis kyang nad thams cad kyang thar pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-17: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i rin chen rigs kyi rigs lnga phye ba'i gnas skabs te lnga ba'o /
T02TD2691E:119a-19: // / kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-20: sems can la thugs rje che ba'i phyir /
T02TD2691E:119a-21: kun dga' bo la smras pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-23: gsang sngags kyi gzhi 'di yang yid la bya'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-24: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo 'di kun gzhi rnam par dag pa /
T02TD2691E:119a-25: thabs shes rab zung du 'jug pa rin po che'i rigs /
T02TD2691E:119a-26: mtshon bya ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
T02TD2691E:119a-27: mtshon byed ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-28: tshor ba'i phung po ni chu'i khams /
T02TD2691E:119a-30: sku mdog dang phyag mtshan gsal ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119a-31: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa sku mdog ser mo //
T02TD2691E:119a-32: dbu la rigs lngas brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:119a-33: spyan gsum pa rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:119a-34: lo bcu gnyis pa'i cha byad can /
T02TD2691E:119a-35: phyag g-yas pa na mchod sbyin mdzad pa /
T02TD2691E:119a-36: g-yon pa na rma bya'i sgro bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-37: zhabs phyed skyil du bzhugs pa /
T02TD2691E:119a-38: padma'i steng na zla ba'i gdan /
T02TD2691E:119a-39: nyi ma'i 'od zer dang ldan pa /
T02TD2691E:119a-40: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin de lta bu'i rig sngags yid la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-41: 'di yid la byas par gyur na glags tshol ba rnams kyis kyang glags mi rnyed do //
T02TD2691E:119a-42: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:119a-44: tsi li mi li la sogs ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119a-45: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-0: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pas 'gro ba @119b rigs drug gi don du kun dga' bo la gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-1: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa'i rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-2: 'das pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis kyang rjes su yi rang zhing srung ba ste /
T02TD2691E:119b-3: de bzhin du ma 'ongs pa rnams kyis kyang srung bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:119b-4: da ltar yod pa rnams kyis kyang srung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-5: de bzhin drug pa la sogs pa gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed stong phrag brgyad khri rnams kyis kyang srung ste /
T02TD2691E:119b-6: de yang rang rang gi gzi brjid kyis srung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-7: rang gi gzi brjid ni gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:119b-8: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gzi brjid dang ;
T02TD2691E:119b-9: / gtsug tor can gyi stobs rnams dang //
T02TD2691E:119b-10: thams cad skyob kyi bden tshig dang //
T02TD2691E:119b-11: log dad sel gyi ting 'dzin dang /
T02TD2691E:119b-12: gser thub kyi ni ye shes dang //
T02TD2691E:119b-15: byams pa mgon pos shes rab bstan//
T02TD2691E:119b-17: de bzhin rig sngags rim bzhin srungs //
T02TD2691E:119b-18: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo 'di yang mthu che zhing sems can rnams la thugs rjes khyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-19: srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-20: gang zag sems can thams cad la'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-21: yongs su sba ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-22: rig sngags kyi don gsang bar byas ba sba ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-24: 'jigs pa thams cad las sbas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-25: yongs su bskyab pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-26: 'jig rten 'di'i sdug bsngal las yongs su bskyab pa dang /
T02TD2691E:119b-27: ngan song gsum las yongs su bskyab pa dang /
T02TD2691E:119b-28: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi 'jigs pa las bskyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-29: yongs su gzung ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-30: ma rig pa'i zhen pas mi dge ba bcu'i lam la 'jug pa ste /
T02TD2691E:119b-31: der 'gror ma ster bas na yongs su gzung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-32: yang na 'khor bar 'gro 'dod pa rams gzung bar bya 'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-33: yongs su bskyang ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-34: rig sngags kyi ye shes kyis ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal ba ste /
T02TD2691E:119b-35: rang bzhin 'od gsal gyi ye shes kyis bsal ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-36: zhi ba dang bde legs su 'gyur ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:119b-38: 'jig rten gyi sdug bsngal zhi ba'o //
T02TD2691E:119b-39: nor phun sum tshogs pa dang /
T02TD2691E:120a-3: nad thams cad dang bral zhing 'byung bo 'am mi'am cab cob kyi 'jigs pa mi 'byung zhing tshe phyi ma la yang de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:120a-4: chad pa spang ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-7: gshin rje la sogs pa'i chad pa spang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:120a-8: mtshon cha spang pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-10: gzhan yang long med par 'byung ba'am /
T02TD2691E:120a-11: de rnams thams cad spang bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:120a-12: dug gzhil ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-13: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo'i gzi brjid kyis 'gro ba'i dug dang bsdad pa'i dug dang byas pa'i dug dang gsum zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:120a-14: dug gsad pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-16: de yang nad gi dug dang phyi'i dug go //
T02TD2691E:120a-17: nang gi dug ni gti mug dad /
T02TD2691E:120a-20: phyi'i dug ni mche ba rtsa ba la sbyor ba'o //
T02TD2691E:120a-21: mtshams gcad pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-22: phyogs mtshams brgyad dang bcu gcad de /
T02TD2691E:120a-23: de las gcad pas na mtshams gcad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:120a-24: sa bcing ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-25: sa la rgyu ba'i 'byung po la sogs pa rnams la yang bcing ba'o //
T02TD2691E:120a-26: lo brgya 'tsho bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-27: sdug bsngal dang bral zhing phun sum tshogs pas lo brgyar 'tsho bar 'gyur ba'o //
T02TD2691E:120a-28: ston brgya mthong bar shog shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-29: nad med cing tshe ring ba ste /
T02TD2691E:120a-30: bkra shis shing phongs pa med pa /
T02TD2691E:120a-31: shi ba'i dus su yang rgas pa ma tshor bar 'chi ba'o //
T02TD2691E:120a-32: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-33: bsrung ba'i don du sems can gyi sdug bsngal la bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2691E:120a-34: gang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis srung ba byas shing sbas pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120a-35: 'di la gus nas 'chang ba'i gang zag de klog pa dang /
T02TD2691E:120a-38: rjes su yi rang ba dang /
T02TD2691E:120a-42: dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa la sogs pa byas nas yongs su sba ba la sogs pa byed par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:120a-44: thugs rje che zhing mthu che ba ste /
T02TD2691E:120b-4: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la phyag rgya'i rgyas gdab cing sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang rjes su yi rang zhing gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:120b-5: 'jig rten 'di'i lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-6: dmyal ba'i gnas nas gzugs med pa'i khams rnams so //
T02TD2691E:120b-7: dmyal ba la tsha ba'i dmyal ba dang /
T02TD2691E:120b-8: grang ba'i dmyal ba dang gnyis gcig tu brtsis te brgyad do //
T02TD2691E:120b-9: byol song dang yi dgas gnyis te bcu'o //
T02TD2691E:120b-10: mi yul gling bzhi la so sor bgrangs pas bzhi /
T02TD2691E:120b-12: de ni 'jig rten 'dod pa'i khams so //
T02TD2691E:120b-13: bsam gtan dang po nas bzung nas /
T02TD2691E:120b-14: gtsang ma'i ris kyi lha man can ni gzugs khams kyi 'jig rten no //
T02TD2691E:120b-15: skye mched mu bzhi gzugs med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams so //
T02TD2691E:120b-16: de bas na 'jig rten 'di'i lha rnam dang zhes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:120b-17: bdud rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-18: ga ra dbang phyug gi 'khor bdud kyi lha rigs stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:120b-19: tshangs par spyod pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-20: mi mjed kyi 'jig rten gyi khams bdag po tshangs pa nas gzugs khams kyi lha man chad do //
T02TD2691E:120b-21: dge slong dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-22: rab tu byung zhing tshangs par spyod pa'i gzugs snang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:120b-23: bram ze'i lus su skyes pa'am zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-24: mi'i 'jig rten gyi khams su rigs bzang por skyes nas gnas pa rnams so //
T02TD2691E:120b-25: skye dgu'i bdag po rnams zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-26: lha dang mi'i bye brag tu smra ba rnams so //
T02TD2691E:120b-27: lha dang mi dang lha ma yin rnams so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-28: gzhan yang de rnams kyis kyang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la gus par byas nas /
T02TD2691E:120b-29: de rnams la yang bsrung ba dang /
T02TD2691E:120b-32: sa bcing ba las rnam par 'tshe ba'i phyir 'od ba zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:120b-33: 'byung po de rnams dge ba la bar du gcod cing glags tshol ba rnams yin te /
T02TD2691E:120b-34: de ni bdud kyi rang bzhin 'khor ba la gnas par byed pa'i rgyu nad rnams sna tshogs btang ba'i bdag po dang sems can rnams la gnod pa skyel zhing sa dang bar snang sa 'og chu la rgyu ba rnams so //
T02TD2691E:121a-0: de rnams kyi stobs ni ri @121a * //
T02TD2691E:121a-1: rab tsam sgul zhing sa g-yo bar byed do //
T02TD2691E:121a-2: de ni gzugs kyi rang bzhin can yin te /
T02TD2691E:121a-3: yid kyi rang bzhin can no //
T02TD2691E:121a-4: de rnams kyis sems can rnams la glags tshol zhing 'tshe bar byas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-5: lha'am zhes bya ba ni lha'i 'byung po stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-6: lha mo'am zhes bya ba ni lha mo'i gzugs stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-7: lha'i bu'am zhes bya ba ni lha'i bu stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-8: lha'i bu mo'am zhes bya ba ni lha'i bu mo'i gzugs stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-9: lha rgan po'am zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:121a-10: lha rgan po'i gzugs stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-11: lha rgan mo 'am zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:121a-12: lha rgan mo'i gzugs stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-13: lha'i 'khor pho'am zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:121a-14: lha'i 'khor pho'i gzugs stong phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-15: lha'i 'khor mo nas gnon po'i 'khor mo 'am zhes bya ba la sogs pa stong phrag brgyad cu brgyad cu rnams so //
T02TD2691E:121a-16: de rnams kyis glags tshol ba ni ci'i phyir zhe na /
T02TD2691E:121a-17: 'byung po ma rungs pa rnams gzugs sna tshogs su sbrul zhing glags tshol ba'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-18: de dag gi ni mdun rgyug pa //
T02TD2691E:121a-19: 'byung po gnod sbyin lus po che //
T02TD2691E:121a-20: lag pa bzhi pa ma rungs pa //
T02TD2691E:121a-21: rkang mangs dang ni rkang gcig pa //
T02TD2691E:121a-22: rkang bzhi pa la rkang gnyis pa //
T02TD2691E:121a-23: rkang pa bsgreng ba spyi'u tshugs dang //
T02TD2691E:121a-24: lus mang mgo bo gcig pa dang //
T02TD2691E:121a-25: lus gcig pa la mgo bzhi pa //
T02TD2691E:121a-26: mig mang po la lus gcig dang //
T02TD2691E:121a-27: mig gcig lto ni bcu gnyis dang //
T02TD2691E:121a-28: bong bu rnga mo glang chen mgo //
T02TD2691E:121a-29: rkang pa bsgreng la mgo btud dang //
T02TD2691E:121a-30: mtshon cha'i so dang mtshon cha'i lag / mtshon cha'i rkang ba'i srin po rnams //
T02TD2691E:121a-31: zangs kyi skra dang zangs kyi so //
T02TD2691E:121a-32: zangs kyi mig dang zangs kyi lag / zangs kyi tho ba'i rkang pa dang //
T02TD2691E:121a-33: zangs kyi sna dang lcags kyi kha //
T02TD2691E:121a-34: rkang lag kun du 'bar ba dang //
T02TD2691E:121a-35: mi yi lus su gnas pa rnams //
T02TD2691E:121a-36: sgur zhar lba ba gsum yod pa //
T02TD2691E:121a-37: mig mi sdug la kha glal ba //
T02TD2691E:121a-38: chu srin stag gi gzugs dang ni //
T02TD2691E:121a-39: gzugs mi sdug dang kha ral bo //
T02TD2691E:121a-40: mchu 'phyangs po dang so yon po //
T02TD2691E:121a-41: rab tu gtum po khro gnyer can //
T02TD2691E:121a-42: gsus po che dang bum sna'o //
T02TD2691E:121a-43: sna 'phyangs po dang rna ba med //
T02TD2691E:121b-0: lag rings po dang @121b rna ba ring //
T02TD2691E:121b-1: sna yi rtse dang lag rtse ring //
T02TD2691E:121b-2: lus skams lus ni ring ba dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-3: skra ring rab tu brgyan pa dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-4: rkang pa mid pa phra ba dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-5: dri nga ba dang bum lto bo //
T02TD2691E:121b-6: yan lag chu srin 'dra ba dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-7: gtun shing tho ba 'dra ba'i lto //
T02TD2691E:121b-8: gnam lto bo la rna bo che //
T02TD2691E:121b-9: gyen du skra brdzes rab tu dmar//
T02TD2691E:121b-10: mgo bo che la gzhu mgrin po //
T02TD2691E:121b-11: skem po sgur po bum lto bo //
T02TD2691E:121b-12: ri rab rtse mo bsgul nas su //
T02TD2691E:121b-13: me mdag gi ni char pa 'bebs //
T02TD2691E:121b-14: ljon shing ri yi rdo ba dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-15: sprin gyi tshogs kyi mdog 'dra ba //
T02TD2691E:121b-16: dung dang rnga chen rdza rnga dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-17: grul bum rnga chen rnams kyi sgra //
T02TD2691E:121b-19: mig po che la bong bu'i sgra //
T02TD2691E:121b-20: nag po sngon po ser po dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-21: dmar ser me dang dmar ser dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-22: khab 'dra'i spu dang ral gri'i skra //
T02TD2691E:121b-23: dmar po'i khrag gis bskus pa rnams //
T02TD2691E:121b-24: mi ro dag ni khyer nas su //
T02TD2691E:121b-25: za bzhin du ni rnam par rgyug / so rnon lag pa dmar ba dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-26: mchu ni khrag gis bskus pa dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-27: lus phyed dag ni zos pa dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-28: mkhal ma snying dang nang grol gyis //
T02TD2691E:121b-29: snyim pa shin tu bkang ba dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-30: byis pa dag ni za bzhin du //
T02TD2691E:121b-31: mer mer po dang srog chags kyi //
T02TD2691E:121b-32: rkang lag rnams kyi stobs kyang 'phrog / ked [*keng?] rus kyi ni lus kyis su //
T02TD2691E:121b-33: skye bo mang po skrag par byed //
T02TD2691E:121b-34: khrag gis rab tu bkang ba yi //
T02TD2691E:121b-35: mi yi bags pa thogs nas su //
T02TD2691E:121b-36: mi bzad dug gis kun bskus te //
T02TD2691E:121b-37: phyogs phyogs dag tu rnam par rgyug / grong khyer rnams kyi sgo dag dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-38: khyim nas khyim du rnam par 'thor //
T02TD2691E:121b-39: rlung dang bad kan mkhris pa rnams //
T02TD2691E:121b-40: phyogs bzhi dag tu 'khrug par byed //
T02TD2691E:121b-41: de ltar de ni rgyal po yi //
T02TD2691E:121b-42: gdon dang 'jigs pa chen po rnams //
T02TD2691E:121b-43: lhags ba de dag thams cad kyang //
T02TD2691E:121b-44: 'byung po de dag rnams kyis kyang //
T02TD2691E:121b-45: glags tshol ba yi dus su yang //
T02TD2691E:121b-46: mi'i 'jig rten 'di la rmi lam dang rtags bstan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:121b-47: phyogs bcu dag tu 'jigs pa skyed //
T02TD2691E:121b-48: bud med dag dang skyes pa dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-49: de bzhin khye'i [?] bu mo dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-50: mngal na gnas pa'ang 'jigs pa skyed //
T02TD2691E:121b-52: skar ma dag dang nyi zla dang //
T02TD2691E:121b-53: gtum pa'i gza' rnams gnod par bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-0: @122a * // lo tog sa bon 'bras bu dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-1: me tog sman dang zas skom dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-2: mi rnams kyi ni dpal 'phrog cing //
T02TD2691E:122a-3: mthon po rnams kyang dma' bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-4: 'jig rten dag na nongs pa rnams //
T02TD2691E:122a-5: dmag dang 'thab mo sha gnyer dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-6: tshig gam zhig gam gsad bya ba //
T02TD2691E:122a-7: de kun 'byung po'i rnam pas gyur //
T02TD2691E:122a-8: sbed cing slar yang bgyid pa dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-9: bzlog par bgyid cing dgod par bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-10: 'jigs par bgyid cing lta bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-11: dgrar 'gyur ba yang ston par bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-12: sdig pa'i rmi lam mthong bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-13: nyal ba dag la gnod par bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-14: sgo nas se gol sgra 'byung zhing //
T02TD2691E:122a-15: mi snyan brjod de za bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-16: mdza' bo gnyen bshes gzugs dag tu //
T02TD2691E:122a-17: gda' zhing bka' mchid smra bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-18: bu mo sdug gu'i gzugs dag tu //
T02TD2691E:122a-19: 'dod la spyod la dga' bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-20: nyi ma skar ma'i gzugs dag dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-21: zla ba'i gzugs su gda' bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-22: rlung dang skar mda' lce gzugs su //
T02TD2691E:122a-23: de la gnod pa de dag gda' //
T02TD2691E:122a-24: skar ma'i tshogs dang 'dra ba dag /'jigs par bgyid pa wa dang khyi //
T02TD2691E:122a-25: rnam par sprul nas ljon shing dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-26: mchod rten dag gi gnas na gda' //
T02TD2691E:122a-27: skyes pa gzhon nu'i gzugs mdzes pas //
T02TD2691E:122a-29: gnas rnams dang ni shul dag tu //
T02TD2691E:122a-30: rnam pa sna tshogs rjes kyang ston //
T02TD2691E:122a-31: grong khyer dag na khyim rnams kyi //
T02TD2691E:122a-32: sgo yang gdon chen de dag 'byed //
T02TD2691E:122a-33: srog dang lus kyang blang bgyis shing //
T02TD2691E:122a-34: lam ngan kun du bskor bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-35: rnam pa sna tshogs gzugs dag dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-36: rnam pa sna tshogs sgra rnams dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-37: rnam pa sna tshogs nad kyi rnams //
T02TD2691E:122a-38: lus ni na bar gnas par ston //
T02TD2691E:122a-39: nad rnams kun gyi mtshan nyid kyang //
T02TD2691E:122a-40: phyin ci log tu ston par bgyid //
T02TD2691E:122a-41: ji snyed 'jig rten rang bzhin dag / thams cad log par de dag ston //
T02TD2691E:122a-42: yang na 'byung po de rnams mi'i 'jig rten la gnod par byas nas glags tshol zhing grong ngam grong khyer du rgyu na /
T02TD2691E:122a-43: mtshan nyid de bzhin du yin te //
T02TD2691E:122a-44: grong khyer grong rngal [*rdal] yul 'khor dang //
T02TD2691E:122a-45: pho brang 'khor du rgyu ba ni //
T02TD2691E:122a-46: gnod sbyin ma rungs mdangs 'phrog pa //
T02TD2691E:122a-47: snying rje med cing khrag 'thung ba //
T02TD2691E:122a-48: lus che 'jigs pa chen po ste //
T02TD2691E:122b-0: @122b stobs po che la sgra yang che //
T02TD2691E:122b-1: mgrin bcu po la mig stong po //
T02TD2691E:122b-2: gdon chen mig ni dmar po rnams //
T02TD2691E:122b-3: 'khor ni mang po rnams btang ste //
T02TD2691E:122b-4: lag na mtshon thogs rab tu 'jigs //
T02TD2691E:122b-5: sbrul gyi pags pa thogs pa dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-6: lag bzhi lag na sgron ma thogs //
T02TD2691E:122b-7: lag na mtshon dang dbyug pa thogs //
T02TD2691E:122b-8: rdo rje mdung rtse dbyug pa thogs //
T02TD2691E:122b-9: rab tu drag pa'i dmag rgal nas //
T02TD2691E:122b-10: phyogs kun du ni skrag par byed //
T02TD2691E:122b-11: sdang ba'i gnas na 'khod pa yi //
T02TD2691E:122b-12: gsang ba po ni dad kun kyang //
T02TD2691E:122b-14: skyes pa bud med gzhan yang 'dzin //
T02TD2691E:122b-15: sha khrag dron por bcas pa la //
T02TD2691E:122b-17: seng ge dang ni stag dang rta //
T02TD2691E:122b-18: ma he ba lang bong bu rnga //
T02TD2691E:122b-19: glang po che yi gzugs 'dra dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-20: dom dang gzig dang sbyang ki dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-21: khyi dang wa dang ra dag dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-22: byi la byi ba sbre'u yi gzugs //
T02TD2691E:122b-23: bse dang phag dang sre mo dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-24: nya dang rus sbal dag gi gzugs //
T02TD2691E:122b-25: kha cig dag ni sram gyi gzugs //
T02TD2691E:122b-26: khva dang 'ug pha khu byug dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-27: bya rgod khra dang nya mid bcas //
T02TD2691E:122b-28: rma bya ngang ba thi ba dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-29: khrung khrung dang ni bya rnams dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-30: kha cig bya gag gzugs rnams su //
T02TD2691E:122b-31: gnod sbyin rnams ni mi yis mthong //
T02TD2691E:122b-32: 'dab bzangs bya yi tshul gyis kyang //
T02TD2691E:122b-33: skye bo mang po skrag par byed //
T02TD2691E:122b-34: kha cig mi yi mgo can la //
T02TD2691E:122b-35: lus ni bya gag bong bu 'dra //
T02TD2691E:122b-36: kha cig mtshon gyis rab tu 'tshe //
T02TD2691E:122b-37: lus dang bral ba dag tu snang //
T02TD2691E:122b-39: rgyu ma'i phreng bas kun du dkris //
T02TD2691E:122b-40: rtse gsum mdung gis rab 'debs shing //
T02TD2691E:122b-41: srog chags rnams la gnod par byed //
T02TD2691E:122b-42: mi bzad pa yi dbugs 'byin zhing //
T02TD2691E:122b-43: skye dgu 'di dag skrag par byed //
T02TD2691E:122b-44: srog chags rgyud ni ji snyed pa //
T02TD2691E:122b-45: sna tshogs kyi ni gzugs su snang //
T02TD2691E:122b-46: kha cig dag ni ri yang thogs ;
T02TD2691E:122b-47: ; la la ral gri 'khor lo thogs //
T02TD2691E:122b-48: grangs ni brgya phrag stong gnas te //
T02TD2691E:122b-49: dbyug pas bsdigs shing kha drag po //
T02TD2691E:122b-50: mig phyung ba la bzhin mi sdug / srin po'i gzugs ni sngo ba dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-51: sna dang rna ba bcad pa dang //
T02TD2691E:122b-52: lce bcad gdong ni gnyer ma can //
T02TD2691E:123a-2: mgo bo bcad pa'i srin po rnams //
T02TD2691E:123a-3: skabs ni rab tu tshol bar byed //
T02TD2691E:123a-4: sdig pa can rnams gzi brjid 'phrog / mi dag gi ni lus rnams la //
T02TD2691E:123a-5: rab tu phra ba'i gdon du snang //
T02TD2691E:123a-6: spu yi bar dang gnad rnams dang //
T02TD2691E:123a-7: de bzhin rma yi kha rnams su //
T02TD2691E:123a-8: lhags pa de dag thams cad kyang //
T02TD2691E:123a-9: de bzhin du lha pho mo dang /
T02TD2691E:123a-10: klu pho mo dang gnod sbyin pho mo la sogs pas skad cig thang cig la /
T02TD2691E:123a-11: sems can la 'tshe bar byed pa nad sna tshogs gtong zhing 'byung po rnams kyis kyang glags tshol ba'o //
T02TD2691E:123a-12: glags tshol bar 'dod cing glags lta na yang glags mi rnyed de zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:123a-13: lha'i gdon dang bcas pa'i 'byung po rnams kyis kyang gnod par byed mi nus shing /
T02TD2691E:123a-15: glags tshol ba lta ci smos so //
T02TD2691E:123a-17: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di /
T02TD2691E:123a-18: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis /
T02TD2691E:123a-19: rjes su yi rang zhing gsungs pa //
T02TD2691E:123a-20: gzi brjid che ba stobs dang ldan pa /
T02TD2691E:123a-21: 'byung po rnams kyi gnyen por gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:123a-22: de bas na glags tshol bas mi rnyed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:123a-23: lha ni lha 'du ba'i gnas su ma yin zhes bya ba la sogs pa nas /
T02TD2691E:123a-24: gnon po ni gnon po 'du ba'i gnas su ma yin no zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:123a-25: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid kyis 'du bar mi nus shing 'byung po rnams kyang so sor 'khyams te /
T02TD2691E:123a-27: rtsar nye bar mi nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:123a-28: gang la la zhig rig sngags 'di las 'gal bar byed na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:123a-29: gal te glags tshol ba rnams rig sngags kyi bka' las 'das par gyur na /
T02TD2691E:123a-30: sdug bsngal dpag tu med pa 'thob ste /
T02TD2691E:123a-31: dmyal ba mnar med du skye bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:123a-32: dmyal ba de las thon nas yang nas yang du gzhan du dmyal bar 'pho'o //
T02TD2691E:123a-33: de'i mgo bo aardza ka'i dog pa bzhin du tshal pa bdun du 'gas so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:123a-34: rig sngags kyi dmod mos mdze 'am phol mig gam /
T02TD2691E:123a-35: lhog pa'am 'bras la sogs pa rnams kyis btab nas /
T02TD2691E:123a-36: shi ba'i dus su tshol ba bdun du 'gas so //
T02TD2691E:123b-0: gsang sngags kyi gzhi dag kyang yid la bya'o zhes bya ba ni 'byung po rnams @123b kyi gnyen po ni /
T02TD2691E:123b-1: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i gsang sngags kyi thabs bshad par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:123b-2: slob dpon las kyi rdo rjes tshigs su bcad pa 'di gsungs so //
T02TD2691E:123b-8: rig sngags kyi nga rgyal byas nas /
T02TD2691E:123b-9: phyag g-yas g-yon gyis dgug pa'i phyag rgya bya ste /
T02TD2691E:123b-10: rdo rje khu tshur yang dag par bcas la /
T02TD2691E:123b-11: mdzub mo gnyis kyis dgug pa'i tshul du'o //
T02TD2691E:123b-12: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags la /
T02TD2691E:123b-13: aom badzra aam ku sha dza: la rig sngags kyi gsang sngags btags la dgug par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:123b-15: aom dang rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi //
T02TD2691E:123b-16: rig sngags smon gyis 'dug mi nus //
T02TD2691E:123b-17: ri rab dur khrod pho brang dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-18: rgya mtsho lung stong shing gcig dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-19: nags tshal dag dang rgya gram dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-20: ri yi rtse mo mchod rten rtsa //
T02TD2691E:123b-21: khron pa dag dang chu mig dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-22: mtsho chen dang ni tshal gnas dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-23: de bzhin grong khyer grong gnas dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-24: grong rdal dang ni pho brang dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-25: ri yi rtse mo nam mkha' dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-26: bar snang chu dang sa la gnas //
T02TD2691E:123b-27: de bzhin sa 'og lam la gnas //
T02TD2691E:123b-28: dza: h'um bam ho: 'i phyag rgya yis //
T02TD2691E:123b-29: 'byung po mang po rig sngags dgug /'byung po ma rungs pa rnams rig sngags kyi phyag rgyas dgug pa'o //
T02TD2691E:123b-31: yungs kar ske tshe dang bsres la /
T02TD2691E:123b-32: ra bar tsher ma can gyi shing bu ste /
T02TD2691E:123b-33: mdzod dang khyim gyi phyogs mtshams kyis blangs la ske tshe dang yungs kar bsres la yang bden pa'i tshigs bcad bton la /
T02TD2691E:123b-34: bde gshegs rnams kyi gzi brjid kyis //
T02TD2691E:123b-35: gtsug tor can gyi stobs rnams dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-36: thams cad skyob pa'i bden tshig dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-37: log dang sel gyi ting 'dzin dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-38: gser thub kyi ni ye shes kyis //
T02TD2691E:123b-41: 'byung po de dag brlag par shog / au tsa ta ya phat rnams kyis //
T02TD2691E:123b-42: rig sngags snying po de btags la //
T02TD2691E:123b-43: rnga bo che dang 'khar rnga dang //
T02TD2691E:123b-44: de la sogs pa sgra yi tshogs //
T02TD2691E:123b-45: de brdungs 'byung po bskrad par bya //
T02TD2691E:124a-2: rtsa ba sna tshogs lo ma dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-3: 'bru sna chu dang bcas pa dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-4: 'ongs pa'i phyogs su bskyal bar bya //
T02TD2691E:124a-5: de bzhin bskrad nas mnan par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:124a-6: gro ga la sogs shing lo la //
T02TD2691E:124a-8: de yi nang du ming byang bri //
T02TD2691E:124a-9: yungs kar lan tshva ske tshe dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-10: shang tshe dug rdzas ro thang dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-11: de rnams bcug la dril bar bya //
T02TD2691E:124a-12: rabs chad mdze thod nang du gzhug / sngar bshad dgug gzhug 'byung po la //
T02TD2691E:124a-13: rig sngags la ni stambha ya gdags //
T02TD2691E:124a-14: lam mam rgya gram mchod rten 'og / pho khrom sar ni mnan par bya //
T02TD2691E:124a-15: de bzhin mnan la bsreg par bya //
T02TD2691E:124a-16: tsandan la sogs dri rnams kyi //
T02TD2691E:124a-17: de yi chus ni lus rnams bkru //
T02TD2691E:124a-18: smyung bar byas nas gos gtsang gyon //
T02TD2691E:124a-19: seng ldeng shing la zhugs phul la //
T02TD2691E:124a-20: 'bru dang rtsa ba sna tshogs dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-21: gnod byed gang la ming btags la //
T02TD2691E:124a-22: zhugs kyi nang du gtor bar bgyi //
T02TD2691E:124a-23: gsang sngags la ni me sngags gdags //
T02TD2691E:124a-24: 'byung po'i rnam pa ma lus bsreg / gtor ma me tog lo ma dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-25: chos skyong la ni sbyin par bya //
T02TD2691E:124a-26: de nas bden pa'i tshig bshad 'di //
T02TD2691E:124a-27: yang dag gis ni brjod par bya //
T02TD2691E:124a-28: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzi brjid kyis //
T02TD2691E:124a-29: rang rgyal dag gi gzi brjid dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-30: dgra bcom pa yi mthu dag gis //
T02TD2691E:124a-31: gsang sngags 'dzin pa thams cad dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-32: sh'a ri'i bu yi shes rab dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-33: mood gal bu yi rdzu 'phrul dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-34: ma 'gags pa yi mig dang ni //
T02TD2691E:124a-35: 'od srungs sbyangs pa'i yon tan dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-37: kun dga' bo yi thos pa dang ;
T02TD2691E:124a-38: ; tshangs pa yi ni byams pa dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-39: brgya byin gyi ni dbang rnams dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-40: 'jig rten skyong ba'i yul rnams thob //
T02TD2691E:124a-41: dbang phyug chen po'i stobs dag dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-42: ded dpon rnams kyi mthu dag gis //
T02TD2691E:124a-44: de dag rnams kyi mthu dag gis //
T02TD2691E:124a-45: bdag gi gnod byed bsreg par shog /'byung po dug dang dgra bo dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-46: bdag gi 'jigs pa thams cad dang //
T02TD2691E:124a-47: sangs rgyas bden pa de rnams kyis //
T02TD2691E:124a-48: sems can dag dang bdag rnams dang //
T02TD2691E:124b-0: sdig pa thams cad bsreg par shog / gsang sngags tshig rnams bden @124b par shog / de bzhin du yang nas yang du gsang sngags la me'i sngags btags la bsreg par bgyi'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-1: de nas rig sngags ni gang zhe na kun gzhi rnam par dag pa ste /
T02TD2691E:124b-2: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-3: mtshon pa ni me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
T02TD2691E:124b-4: mtshon byed ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-6: rnam par shes pa'i phung po'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-9: zhe sdang gi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:124b-10: sangs rgyas rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan no //
T02TD2691E:124b-11: spyan gsum pa zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
T02TD2691E:124b-12: khro gnyer can kha gdangs pa /
T02TD2691E:124b-16: yan lag thams cad rin po che dang sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:124b-17: sham thabs stag gis byas pa /
T02TD2691E:124b-18: g-yas dang po na rdo rje rtse lnga gdengs pa /
T02TD2691E:124b-19: de'i 'og ma na ni ral gri / g-yon dang po na sdigs mdzub dang zhags pa /
T02TD2691E:124b-21: zhabs g-yas bskum pa g-yon brkyang ba gnyis na ma rungs pa'i 'byung po thams cad mnan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-22: nyi ma'i gdan la me yi 'od /
T02TD2691E:124b-24: me ltar 'bar ba rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan de ni thod pas brgyan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-25: dbu'i spyi bo'i gtsug na rma bya'i sgro lngas brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:124b-26: de ni ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:124b-27: padma'i gdan la bzhugs shing khro mor bsam mo //
T02TD2691E:124b-28: de bzhin du rig sngags kyi gsang sngags yid la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-29: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags kyi tshig ni gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:124b-31: ai li mi li ki li la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-33: shi ba'i dus su mgo bo tshal par 'gas shing /
T02TD2691E:124b-34: shi ma thag mnar med par 'gro ba'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-35: bdag la bsrung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni gang zag sems can rnams la'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-36: sba ba dang yongs su bskyab pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
