T02TD2691E:124b-37: khams gsum na rgyu ba'i 'byung po thams cad sba ba'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-38: de bzhin du bskyab pa yang yin no //
T02TD2691E:124b-39: yongs su gzung ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:124b-40: dper na rang gi nor gzhan du mi ster ba bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:124b-41: 'byung po de rnams la yang mi ster ba'o //
T02TD2691E:124b-42: yongs su bskyang ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:125a-1: sngags kyi rgyal mo'i gzi brjid kyis /
T02TD2691E:125a-2: glang chen smyon pa bzhin du thub pa med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-3: zhi ba dang zhes bya ba ni 'byung po thams cad dang nad zhi bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-4: bde legs su 'gyur ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:125a-5: bkra shis shing nad rnams bcom pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-6: chad pa spang ba dang zhes bya ba ni 'byung po de rnams kyis glags tshol bar 'dod pas glags mi rnyed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-7: mtshon cha sbang ba dang zhes bya ba ni //
T02TD2691E:125a-8: rig sngags kyi dmod mos 'byung po de rnams la nus pa med de gzi brjid 'phrog pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-9: dug gzhil ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:125a-10: 'byung po rnams kyi kha rlangs kyi dug reg pa dang mthong ba rnams so //
T02TD2691E:125a-11: dug gsad pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:125a-12: de'i rang bzhin gyi dug phyung ste /
T02TD2691E:125a-13: rig sngags kyi dmod mos dug gsad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-14: mtshams gcad pa dang zhes bya ba ni 'byung po de rnams la gcad de /
T02TD2691E:125a-15: rig sngags 'di'i gzi brjid kyis dpag tshad gcig gi bar du 'ong bar mi nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-16: sa bcing ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:125a-17: sa 'og tu mnan cing dpag tshad gcig tu 'ong bar mi nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-18: lo brgya 'tsho bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni 'byung po de rnams kyi sdug bsngal bral zhing /
T02TD2691E:125a-19: dus ma yin par 'chi ba med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-20: ston brgya mthong bar shog shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:125a-21: yang nas yang du tshe bsnan cing nad rnams kyis mi tshugs te /
T02TD2691E:125a-22: bkra shis shing tshe ring ba'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-23: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i 'byung po rnams glags tshol 'dod pa ma rnyed pa'i skabs te drug pa'o /
T02TD2691E:125a-25: // /'di lta ste zhes bya ba ni 'og tu lta ste 'og tu gang bltas she na /
T02TD2691E:125a-27: ma 'ongs pa dang da ltar yod pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis rjes su yi rang zhing byin gyis brlabs pa /
T02TD2691E:125a-28: dgra bcom nyan thos rnams kyis kyang rjes su yi rang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:125a-29: 'jig rten gyi lha dang bcas pa yang /
T02TD2691E:125a-30: tshangs pa dang brgya byin dang /
T02TD2691E:125a-31: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po mthu chen sum cu rtsa gnyis dang mthu chen po nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
T02TD2691E:125a-32: rgyal po chen po bzhi dang /
T02TD2691E:125a-34: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po sor mo lnga pa dang /
T02TD2691E:125a-35: 'phrog ma'i bu lnga brgya dang bcas pa yang lha'i gdon la sogs pa /
T02TD2691E:125b-0: bgegs @125b dang 'byung po'i rigs su gyur pa stong phrag brgyad cu phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-1: gzhan yang de lta bu rnams kyi rjes su yi rang zhing gnyen por gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-2: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags kyis gso ba'i sman dang /
T02TD2691E:125b-3: gsang sngags kyi tshig ni gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:125b-4: 'dir ni dug gi rang bzhin gyis zas ma legs pa 'byung ba ste /
T02TD2691E:125b-5: zas ma legs pa ni rnam par rtog pa las 'byung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-6: rnam par rtog pa ni dug lnga'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-7: dug lnga ni gti mug yin te /
T02TD2691E:125b-8: gti mug gi rang bzhin gyis zhe sdang byung ngo //
T02TD2691E:125b-9: zhe sdang las 'dod chags byung ngo //
T02TD2691E:125b-10: 'dod chags las nga rgyal byung ngo //
T02TD2691E:125b-11: nga rgyal las phrag dog byung ngo //
T02TD2691E:125b-12: de lnga 'dus pas 'jig rten gyi dug gsum la 'dus te /
T02TD2691E:125b-13: 'jig rten gyi dug gsum ni 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti mug dang gsum mo //
T02TD2691E:125b-14: de'i rang bzhin gyis 'khor ba'i rgyu ste /
T02TD2691E:125b-15: 'khor ba la phyi'i dug gsum byung ngo //
T02TD2691E:125b-16: phyi'i dug gsum ni 'jig rten pa'i las las byung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-17: de yang 'gro ba dang bsdad pa dang byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-18: 'gro ba'i dug ni bsam pa dang /
T02TD2691E:125b-19: mthong ba dang reg pa dang kha rlangs so //
T02TD2691E:125b-20: bsam pa la yang gnyis te /
T02TD2691E:125b-23: reg pa la yang gnyis te /
T02TD2691E:125b-24: nga rgyal gyis reg tu 'gro ba dang /
T02TD2691E:125b-25: rang bzhin gyis dbang du med par reg tu 'jug pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-26: mthong ba la yang gnyis te /
T02TD2691E:125b-27: rang dad pas mthong ba dang /
T02TD2691E:125b-29: kha rlangs la yang gnyis te /
T02TD2691E:125b-31: dbugs rang bzhin gyis dpag tshad gnyis gnyis la slebs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-32: de'i rim pa bzhin du rigs la yang /
T02TD2691E:125b-34: rgyal rigs dang rje'u rigs dang dmangs rigs so //
T02TD2691E:125b-35: de bzhin du yang bram ze'i bram ze dang /
T02TD2691E:125b-38: dmangs rigs kyi dmangs rigs ni gdol ba'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-41: sum cha gcig dang dgongs mo'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-43: sum cha gcig dang tho rangs so //
T02TD2691E:125b-44: rim pa bzhin klu rnams rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:125b-45: bram ze'i rigs kyis sdang dro zin na ni //
T02TD2691E:125b-46: nad bdag kan gyi dus yin te /
T02TD2691E:125b-47: gcong dang tshigs rnams na zhing mig ser te /
T02TD2691E:126a-2: rgyal po'i dus ni nyi ma phyed yin te /
T02TD2691E:126a-4: mchin pa la nad babs shing mig dmar ba'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-5: ro stod mi bde zhing mgo na ba ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-6: lhog pa dang 'bras dang tshad pa skye bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:126a-7: nyi ma sum cha ni rje'u rigs kyi dus yin te /
T02TD2691E:126a-8: nad chu ser gyi dus so //
T02TD2691E:126a-9: grang shum byed cing lus po thams cad 'dar ba'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-11: sha bkra dang tshigs na zhing mkhal ma skrang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-12: dmangs rigs kyi dus ni dgongs mo ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-13: mgo mjid [?] rengs shing na ba ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-14: rkan 'khal zhing skad 'gags te rna ba 'on zhing mig dmar /
T02TD2691E:126a-16: mig 'gul zhing lus po thams cad 'gul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-17: lus po skabs skabs su sbrid cing rkang lag lji ba ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-18: snying mi dga' zhing lus po grang /
T02TD2691E:126a-19: sha ror song zhing shu ba 'byung ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-20: skra rnams 'byi zhing lus po skrangs ba'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-21: rus pa dang rkang las byung ba ni /
T02TD2691E:126a-22: yang dmangs rigs kyi nad yin te /
T02TD2691E:126a-23: lus po skam zhing dang ga 'gags pa ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-24: sme ba 'byung zhing g-yan pa'i nad kyis thebs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-25: de bzhin du rigs gzhan la yang shes par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-26: 'gro ba'i dug ni klu'i rigs yin te /
T02TD2691E:126a-27: mche ba'i dug kyang klu'i rigs shes te /
T02TD2691E:126a-28: sems can las shes par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-29: yang bsdad pa'i dug la rtsa ba dang lo ma las byung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-30: rtsa ba las byung ba ni btsan dug dang /
T02TD2691E:126a-39: de la lo ma'i dug ni de rnams kyi lo ma'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-40: de zos pa'i nad ni shi ba dang /
T02TD2691E:126a-45: de ni bsdad pa'i dug gi nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-46: da byed pa'i dug ni rgya tsha shing kun dang sums pa'i sha'o //
T02TD2691E:126a-47: de'i nad kyis snying mi dga' ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-49: bod phrug gi sha dang 'ug pa'i sha shing kun dang ngo //
T02TD2691E:126a-50: de yan lag la babs te /
T02TD2691E:126a-51: grang shum byed cing tsha ba skye ste /
T02TD2691E:126a-55: de lus la babs te rus pa 'gags par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:126b-0: yang na zas @126b mi legs pa yang sbyor pa'i dug yin te /
T02TD2691E:126b-1: sbrang rtsi dang mar gnyis mnyam por byas nas 'khar phor gyi nang du zhag bdun bzhag ste /
T02TD2691E:126b-2: de yang byed pa'i dug go //
T02TD2691E:126b-3: mkhris pa la tsha ba btang na de yang dug yin te /
T02TD2691E:126b-4: rlung la grang ba gtang ba yang dug go //
T02TD2691E:126b-5: 'jig rten pa'i dug 'di ni rang bzhin rang las 'byung ste /
T02TD2691E:126b-6: ma rig pa'i rang bzhin gyis rang la rang gnod pa'o //
T02TD2691E:126b-7: slob dpon las kyi rdo rjes tshigs su bcad de gsungs pa /
T02TD2691E:126b-8: gti mug dang ni 'dod chags dang //
T02TD2691E:126b-9: zhe sdang rang bzhin rang dug ste //
T02TD2691E:126b-11: phyi yi dug kyang de las byung //
T02TD2691E:126b-12: 'gro dang bsdad dang sbyor ba dang //
T02TD2691E:126b-13: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gyis //
T02TD2691E:126b-14: phyi yi dug ni 'joms par nus //
T02TD2691E:126b-15: rig sngags gzi brjid de 'joms nus //
T02TD2691E:126b-16: gti mug 'dod chags zhe sdang dang //
T02TD2691E:126b-17: rang gi sems kyis bcom pa la //
T02TD2691E:126b-18: gzhan gyis de ni mi choms so //
T02TD2691E:126b-19: bdag gis de ni bor bar bgyi //
T02TD2691E:126b-21: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo dug gi gnyen po 'di /
T02TD2691E:126b-22: dug gsum gso ba la yang dag par nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:126b-23: gsang sngags dang sman dang ting nge 'dzin gyi bye brag gis gso bar bya ba'o //
T02TD2691E:126b-25: nad pa la rig sngags kyi rgyal mo'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs la /
T02TD2691E:126b-26: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags la 'jug pa'o //
T02TD2691E:126b-30: ram nye ba'i rtsa ba'i khu ba dang /
T02TD2691E:126b-32: grang ba chen tsha ba gsum dang /
T02TD2691E:126b-33: tsha dang bsres pa sbrang rtsis sbyar la btang ngo //
T02TD2691E:126b-34: chu ser babs na thal ka rdo rje dang /
T02TD2691E:126b-36: se 'brum gyi phyi skogs dang bsres la btang ngo //
T02TD2691E:126b-37: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags zhag bdun bsgrub par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:126b-38: phol mig dang lus po gas par gyur na mu zi dang mar nag bskol la dug dang 'bras bu gsum dang bsres la ser ka rnams la byug go //
T02TD2691E:126b-39: byab par 'dod na dang po phyag gis bgyi ste /
T02TD2691E:126b-40: gnyis ba rtsva d'ur bas bya'o //
T02TD2691E:126b-41: gsum pa rtsva ku shas te /
T02TD2691E:126b-43: lnga pa rang gi sos dug dbyung ngo //
T02TD2691E:127a-0: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma @127a * //
T02TD2691E:127a-1: bya chen mo'i nga rgyal gyis byas la /
T02TD2691E:127a-13: sha ro la sogs pa'i mdze'i rigs thams cad la de bzhin du bya'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-16: sngar bshad pa'i nag po'i sbyor ba la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-17: ting nge 'dzin mnyam par bzlas pa drag po la 'jug go //
T02TD2691E:127a-18: de bzhin du 'gro ba'i dug gso ba'i bya thabs so //
T02TD2691E:127a-19: bsdad pa'i dug gso ba ni /
T02TD2691E:127a-20: sngo ma h'a ra tsa dang /
T02TD2691E:127a-21: chu grang mo la sbyar nas /
T02TD2691E:127a-24: brgya rtsa brgyad btab la 'thung du gzhug go //
T02TD2691E:127a-25: 'di ni btsan dug dang bong nga nag po'i gnyen po'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-26: ra dug la 'bras bu gsum dang lcags phye btab la /
T02TD2691E:127a-28: rang gi chu la btab la 'thung du gzhug go //
T02TD2691E:127a-29: des ni btsan dug kyang thub po //
T02TD2691E:127a-30: sribs shing gi 'bru gu la 'bras bu gsum gyis bya'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-31: smyo bar gyur na skyur mo'i chu rtsa'am khu ba blud do //
T02TD2691E:127a-32: de ni thang phrom gyi gnyen po'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-33: gas par gyur na mar nag dang /
T02TD2691E:127a-34: gu gul dkar po dang sbyar la byug go //
T02TD2691E:127a-35: skrangs par gyur na thang phrom gyi rtsa ba dang /
T02TD2691E:127a-36: ri sho ba'i rtsa ba dang /
T02TD2691E:127a-37: dug rang dang sbyar la mnan no //
T02TD2691E:127a-38: / gzhan yang thams cad chu grang la btab la btung bar bya'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-39: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i rig sngags kyi gsang sngags bton la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-40: de ni bsdad pa'i dug gso ba'i bcos thabs so //
T02TD2691E:127a-41: da ni byed pa'i dug gso ba ste /
T02TD2691E:127a-42: byed pa'i dug ni sbyor ba'i dug go //
T02TD2691E:127a-43: yungs kar ma tshig par brdos la /
T02TD2691E:127a-44: brdung ba byas la lto stong la gtang ngo //
T02TD2691E:127a-45: de bzhin du zhag gsum bzhi btang bar gyur na /
T02TD2691E:127a-46: lo gcig bar du thub pa'o //
T02TD2691E:127a-47: sha tshan gsum dang skyer ba dang /
T02TD2691E:127a-48: se rgod pa'i bar shun dang /
T02TD2691E:127a-50: ra dmar mo'i khrag dang ri lu byas la btang ngo //
T02TD2691E:127a-51: 'dis ni lo gsum gyi bar du thub ste /
T02TD2691E:127a-52: lo gcig the tshom mi za bar thub bo //
T02TD2691E:127b-0: sha dug byung na sga chung @127b dang tshal chu grang mo la btab la btung ngo //
T02TD2691E:127b-1: rin po che'i dug byung na lcags phye dang /
T02TD2691E:127b-5: dha du ras sbyar la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-6: 'di ni sbyor ba'i dug gso ba'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-7: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di ni 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs pa /
T02TD2691E:127b-8: ma 'ongs pa rnams kyang de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:127b-9: da ltar gyi sh'a kya thub pas gsungs shing rjes su yi rang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-10: thabs shes rab dbyer med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-11: kun gzhi rnam par dag pa'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-12: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes te /
T02TD2691E:127b-13: thabs kyi ngo bo ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo padma'i rigs so //
T02TD2691E:127b-14: phung po ni 'du shes kyi phung po ste /
T02TD2691E:127b-16: skye mched ni lce'i skye mched do //
T02TD2691E:127b-17: rang bzhin ni 'dod chags kyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:127b-18: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2691E:127b-23: yan lag thams cad sbrul gyis brgyan pa dang po'i phyag g-yas g-yon na mtha' yas dang 'jog po'i ngo bor sbrul bsnams pa /
T02TD2691E:127b-24: rig sngags kyi rang bzhin rma bya gser du snang ba gnyis phyag 'og ma gnyis na bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-25: zhabs g-yas bskum pa g-yon brkyang pa'i zhabs kyis padma dang ka ra ru tra mnan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-26: padma'i steng na nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
T02TD2691E:127b-27: nyi ma'i 'od zer dang ldan pa /
T02TD2691E:127b-28: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:127b-29: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pas /
T02TD2691E:127b-30: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las spros pas //
T02TD2691E:127b-31: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di /
T02TD2691E:127b-32: dug gi gnyen po klu'i rgyal po rnams kyi bdag po'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-33: dug gi gnyen po'i snying po ni gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:127b-35: gzhan rnams kyis kyang mi thub cing /
T02TD2691E:127b-36: 'byung po rnams kyi yang gnyen po'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-38: tsid tre tsid tra mu le la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:127b-39: rgyal ba rnams gzigs mya ngan 'tshang la gnas //
T02TD2691E:128a-0: zhes bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs de yang 'khrungs pa'i @128a * //
T02TD2691E:128a-2: shing byang chub kyi shing mya ngan 'tshang gi 'og tu'o //
T02TD2691E:128a-3: sems can gyi don la yul ma ga dh'a la rdo rje gdan la bzhugs pa'i dus su //
T02TD2691E:128a-6: tho rangs sangs rgyas pa'i dus su /
T02TD2691E:128a-7: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo 'di dran par rnyed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:128a-8: de'i bden pas 'gro ba'i dug dang /
T02TD2691E:128a-11: byed pa'i dug nges par bcom mo //
T02TD2691E:128a-12: rgyal ba gtsug tor padma dkar po'i drung //
T02TD2691E:128a-13: zhes bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gtsug tor can ni //
T02TD2691E:128a-14: byang chub kyi shing padma dkar po'i tshal gyi 'og tu 'khrungs te /
T02TD2691E:128a-15: de bzhin du rdo rje gdan la bzhugs pa'i dus su //
T02TD2691E:128a-16: byang chub kyi shing padma dkar po'i 'og tu srod la bdud btul te /
T02TD2691E:128a-17: tho rangs mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so //
T02TD2691E:128a-18: de'i dus su rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di yid la byas te /
T02TD2691E:128a-19: de'i bden pas 'gro ba'i dug dang /
T02TD2691E:128a-20: bsdad pa'i dug dang byed pa'i dug rnams nges par bcom mo //
T02TD2691E:128a-21: thams cad skyob pa s'a la'i drung na gnas //
T02TD2691E:128a-22: zhes bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad skyob de yang 'khrungs pa'i dus su yang shing s'a la'i 'og tu 'khrungs te /
T02TD2691E:128a-23: sems can gyi don la yul ma ga dh'ar /
T02TD2691E:128a-24: rdo rje gdan la bzhugs pa'i dus su byang chub kyi shing s'a la'i 'og tu srod la bdud btul te /
T02TD2691E:128a-25: tho rangs mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so //
T02TD2691E:128a-26: de'i tshe de'i dus na chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong dran pa nye bar gzhag nas /
T02TD2691E:128a-27: sangs rgyas thams cad skyob pas kyang rig sngags gyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di la rjes su yi rangs shing de'i dus su 'gro ba'i dug dang bsdad pa'i dug dang /
T02TD2691E:128a-28: byed pa'i dug nges par bcom mo //
T02TD2691E:128a-29: bram ze 'khor ba 'jig ni shirsha'i drung //
T02TD2691E:128a-30: zhes bya ba ni yul ma gadh'a'i chu bo gangg'a'i lho phyogs kyi 'gram na bram ze mo 'khor ba 'jig ces bya ba ni yum yin te /
T02TD2691E:128a-31: de'i dus su yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas byang chub kyi shing shirsha'i 'og tu sku 'khrungs /
T02TD2691E:128a-32: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs pa'i dus su yang byang chub kyi shing shirsha'i 'og tu'o //
T02TD2691E:128b-0: sems @128b can gyi don du srod la bdud btul te /
T02TD2691E:128b-1: tho rangs mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so //
T02TD2691E:128b-2: de'i dus su yang skad cig mas rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la rjes su yi rangs te /
T02TD2691E:128b-3: sangs rgyas 'khor ba 'jig sems can gyi don la 'gro ba'i dug dang /
T02TD2691E:128b-4: bsdad pa'i dug dang byed pa'i dug nges par bcom mo //
T02TD2691E:128b-5: sangs rgyas gser thub au dumw'a ra'i drung //
T02TD2691E:128b-6: zhes bya ba ni yul ma ga dh'a'i drang srong gi rigs su skyes nas /
T02TD2691E:128b-7: byang chub kyi shing au du mw'a ra'i 'og tu 'khrungs te /
T02TD2691E:128b-8: de bzhin du rdo rje gdan la bzhugs pa'i dus su yang srod la bdud btul zhing tho rang sa mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so //
T02TD2691E:128b-9: de'i dus su yang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la rjes su yi rangs shing bden pa'i tshig gis kyang 'gro ba'i dug dang /
T02TD2691E:128b-10: bsdad ba'i dug dang byed pa'i dug nges par bcom mo //
T02TD2691E:128b-11: 'od srungs n+ya gro dha yi drung na gnas //
T02TD2691E:128b-12: zhes bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srungs 'khrungs pa'i dus su n+ya gro dha'i rtsa bar 'khrungs te /
T02TD2691E:128b-13: rdo rje gdan la bzhugs pa'i dus su yang de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:128b-14: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo 'di la rjes su yi rangs shing rig pa'i nus pas sangs rgyas 'od srungs kyis kyang 'gro ba dang bsdad pa dang /
T02TD2691E:128b-15: byed pa'i dug gsum nges par bcom mo //
T02TD2691E:128b-16: sh'akya thub mchog khyad par gnas drung du //
T02TD2691E:128b-17: zhes bya ba ni grong khyer ser skya'i nang na rgyal po zas gtsang gi sras sems can gyi don la dga' ldan nas yum sgyu ma chen mo'i lhums su zhugs nas 'khrungs pa'i dus su byang chub kyi shing drung gi 'og tu 'khrungs te /
T02TD2691E:128b-18: 'khrungs ma thag tu padma bdun skyes so //
T02TD2691E:128b-19: de yang sems can gyi don la gom pa bdun bor te /
T02TD2691E:128b-20: chu bo nee ranydza ra'i drung du dka' thub lo drug mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:128b-21: gnyis pa rdo rje gdan du byang chub kyi shing gnas kyi drung gi 'og tu /
T02TD2691E:128b-22: rtsva ku sha'i gdan bting nas srod la bdud btul nas tho rangs mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so //
T02TD2691E:128b-23: de'i tshe de'i dus su sngon gyi dran pa nye bar gzhag cing chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong nye bar gzhag nas rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di la rjes su yi rangs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-0: gsum pa w'a r'a na s'ir bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi @129a * //
T02TD2691E:129a-2: bzhi pa mu stegs rigs gcer bu dang rtsod pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-3: lnga pa lha'i yul nas 'dzam bu'i gling du byon nas lha rnams dang spyod pa mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-4: drug pa spre 'us sbrang rtsi phul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-5: bdun pa sku mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-6: dang po dga' ldan nas byon nas yum sgyu ma lha mdzes kyi lhums su zhugs nas btsas pa ni brgyad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-7: de bas na 'khrungs ma thag tu me tog padma brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-8: de'i bden pa dang rig sngags kyir gyal mo'i gzi brjid kyis /
T02TD2691E:129a-9: 'gro ba'i dug dang bsdad pa'i dug dang byed pa'i dug gsum bcom pa'o ;
T02TD2691E:129a-10: ; phyin nas byang chub mchog thob 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:129a-11: goo ta ma zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:129a-12: dus dang po na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs kyi bstan pa ste /
T02TD2691E:129a-13: de'i dus su sa gzhi shel las byas pa 'dzam bu'i gling pa'i tshe tshad kyang stong du gnas so //
T02TD2691E:129a-14: gnyis pa sangs rgyas gtsug tor can gyi bstan pa la sa gzhi ni gser las byas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-15: mi'i tshe lo ni lnga brgya thub po //
T02TD2691E:129a-16: dus gsum pa la sangs rgyas thams cad skyob pa'i bstan pa la sa gzhi ni dngul las byas pa ste //
T02TD2691E:129a-17: mi lo ni phyed dang sum brgya thub pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-18: dus bzhi pa la sangs rgyas log par dad sel gyi bstan pa la /
T02TD2691E:129a-19: sa gzhi ni aindra n'i la las byas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-20: tshe lo brgya nyi shu rtsa lnga'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-21: dus lnga pa la sangs rgyas gser thub yi bstan pa la /
T02TD2691E:129a-22: smon lam stobs kyis gser gyi sa gzhi /
T02TD2691E:129a-23: mi'i tshe lo yang stong tsho gcig go //
T02TD2691E:129a-24: dus drug pa la sangs rgyas 'od srungs kyi bstan pa ste /
T02TD2691E:129a-25: rin po che sna bdun gyis gzhi /
T02TD2691E:129a-26: rin po che sna bdun la longs spyod do //
T02TD2691E:129a-28: dus bdun pa ni tha ma'i dus yin te /
T02TD2691E:129a-29: sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pa'i bstan pa ste /
T02TD2691E:129a-30: sngon gyi dus su sangs rgyas mar me mdzad kyi bstan pa la /
T02TD2691E:129a-31: sangs rgyas nyid la dang po'i smon lam btab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129a-32: de'i tshe de'i dus su sangs rgyas mar me mdzad kyi bstan pa la lha dang lha ma yin sde brgyad dang mi la sogs pa'i sems can gyi mchod pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129b-0: de'i dus su yang sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pa bram ze'i lus su skye nas ni @129b nyi ma'i 'od ces pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129b-1: de'i bu pho zla ba'i 'od du mtshan btags pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129b-2: sangs rgyas mar me mdzad la dad pa skyes nas mchod pa byed du phyin pa lha dang mi la sogs pa mang pos bkag nas ma thar te sangs rgyas zhal yang mthong bar ma thob pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129b-3: sangs rgyas nyid kyis te mngon par shes nas sems can gyi don la char drag po 'bebs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129b-4: sems can thams cad char la gab nas bram ze des sangs rgyas kyi zhal mthong bar gyur to //
T02TD2691E:129b-5: de nas bram ze'i phru gu nyi ma'i 'od kyis sangs rgyas mar me mdzad nags gseb na bzhugs pa la dad pa skyes nas mgo bo'i steng du bzhag go //
T02TD2691E:129b-6: de'i tshe de'i dus su yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mar me mdzad kyis bskal pa tha ma'i dus su yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya seng ger 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan to //
T02TD2691E:129b-7: de ltar yang sa gzhi ni sa'i sa gzhi ste /
T02TD2691E:129b-8: sems can yang bcos dka' ba mtshon sna lnga'i dus //
T02TD2691E:129b-9: chos 'dul ba mngon pa theg pa chen po'i dus /
T02TD2691E:129b-10: pha rol tu phyin pa gsang sngags kyis 'dul ba'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:129b-11: mi'i tshe lo yang brgya nyi shu tham pa /
T02TD2691E:129b-12: gzugs kyang khru phyed dang bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129b-13: de'i dus su yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pa'i bstan pa dar zhing /
T02TD2691E:129b-14: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di la sems can thams cad rjes su yi rangs shing gus par bya ste /
T02TD2691E:129b-15: de'i nus pas kyang dug thams cad bcom pa'o //
T02TD2691E:129b-16: sangs rgyas rdzu 'phrul chen po de dag la //
T02TD2691E:129b-17: zhes bya ba ni sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs dang /
T02TD2691E:129b-24: de'i bden pa dang stobs dang gzi brjid kyis sems can thams cad kyi don byas shing dug bcom mo //
T02TD2691E:129b-25: mngon par dad pa'i lha gang 'khod pa dag ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:129b-26: de dag gi nus pas kyang lha rnams la sogs pas kyang 'di la dad pa bgyis pa gang yang tshe ring zhing nad thams cad dang bral te /
T02TD2691E:129b-27: dug thams cad kyi 'jigs pa las thar bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:130a-1: dga' mgur gyur nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:130a-2: sangs rgyas rnams kyi bden pa dang /
T02TD2691E:130a-3: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid kyis lha dang mi dang lha ma yin la sogs pa bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi po rnams kyang mgu bar gyur cing /
T02TD2691E:130a-4: sems can de la grogs byed par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:130a-5: rtag tu dge zhing zhi bar 'gyur bar byos //
T02TD2691E:130a-6: zhes bya ba ni thog ma tha ma bar du dge bar gyur cig / da ltar yang dug thams cad 'joms shing rig sngags 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:130a-7: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ngag nas byung ste /
T02TD2691E:130a-8: thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa ye shes lnga dang ldan pa /
T02TD2691E:130a-9: 'du shes kyi phung po me'i khams mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes lce'i skye mched zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa sku mdog dmar mo spyan gsum pa /
T02TD2691E:130a-10: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2691E:130a-11: rgyan rnams thams cad sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:130a-12: na bza' la dug gis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:130a-13: klu mtha' yas dang 'jog po mnan pa /
T02TD2691E:130a-14: de bzhin du padma dang padma chen po phyag gis bzung ba /
T02TD2691E:130a-15: nyi ma'i gdan dang 'od dang ldan pa /
T02TD2691E:130a-17: dug bcom pa'i rig sngags gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:130a-18: sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pa'i zhal nas spros pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130a-21: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni /
T02TD2691E:130a-22: ai li mi li ki li la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130a-23: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni dge slong sa ri dang sems can thams cad kyi don du tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la smras pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130a-24: rma bya chen mo 'di dag mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:130a-25: tshangs pa'i lha la sogs pa gzugs khams kyi lha rnams so //
T02TD2691E:130a-26: sman ni rig sngags kyi gsang sngags so //
T02TD2691E:130a-27: bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod du med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130a-28: lha rnams kyi dbang po brgya byin dang zhes bya ba ni 'dod pa'i khams kyi lha sum cu rtsa gsum dang /
T02TD2691E:130a-29: mtshe ma dang dga' ldan dang /
T02TD2691E:130a-30: 'phrul dga' dang gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha rnams kyis kyang rjes su yi rang zhing /
T02TD2691E:130a-32: rgyal po chen po bzhi dang zhes pa ni /
T02TD2691E:130a-33: ri bdun gyi lha rnams dang sman chen por byas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130a-34: gnod sbyin gyi ded dpon nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis bshad pa ste /
T02TD2691E:130b-1: gnod sbyin chen po seng ge'i ral pa can la sogs pa bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu rnams kyis kyang rjes su yi rang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-2: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:130b-3: sangs rgyas kyis yang nas yang du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-4: gang sman chen po 'di dag gi ming 'dzin pa la dga' zhing ;
T02TD2691E:130b-5: rab tu sdang ba'i sems kyis 'ongs na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:130b-6: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i bka' las 'das pa /
T02TD2691E:130b-7: gang sdug bsngal thams cad thob cing dmyal ba mnar med par skye bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:130b-8: de'i mgo bo aardza ka'i dog pa bzhin du tshal pa bdun du 'gas so zhes bya ba ni de'i bka' las 'das pa de'i tshe 'di'i mgo bo 'gas te /
T02TD2691E:130b-9: lus kyang dum bu dum bur zhig go //
T02TD2691E:130b-10: shi nas kyang skyes ma thag tu dmyal ba mnar med pa'i sdug bsngal thob cing /
T02TD2691E:130b-11: de'i sdug bsngal las bral nas kyang /
T02TD2691E:130b-12: dmyal ba padma chen po ltar gas par skye'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-13: rig sngags ni gang zhe na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi spyi bo'i gtsug nas 'phros pa /
T02TD2691E:130b-14: sku'i rang bzhin chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
T02TD2691E:130b-15: gzugs kyi phung po me'i khams /
T02TD2691E:130b-16: mig gi skye mched ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin mtshon bya ni ye shes te /
T02TD2691E:130b-17: de yang shes rab kyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:130b-18: mtshon par byed pa ni thabs so //
T02TD2691E:130b-19: de gnyis su med pa'i sku ni zhal gsum phyag drug sku mdog dmar pa /
T02TD2691E:130b-20: g-yas mthing ga / g-yon ljang gu //
T02TD2691E:130b-21: spyan gsum pa rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2691E:130b-22: lus thams cad sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:130b-24: phyag g-yas dang po na rdo rje /
T02TD2691E:130b-25: 'og ma na rma bya'i sgro bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-26: tha ma na mda' bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-27: g-yon gyi dang po na rin po che /
T02TD2691E:130b-29: tha ma na gzhu bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-30: dug gi me tog gi na bza' gsol ba /
T02TD2691E:130b-31: zhi ba'i tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-32: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni 'di lta ste /
T02TD2691E:130b-34: bka' 'di ni k'i ra ti mu le la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:130b-35: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i dug bcom pa'i gnas skabs te bdun pa'o /
T02TD2691E:130b-37: // / rkang gnyis khyed cag bde legs shog //
T02TD2691E:131a-0: ces bya ba ni 'gro ba rigs drug la @131a * //
T02TD2691E:131a-1: lha'i sdug bsngal la sogs pa de yang bde legs su 'gyur te /
T02TD2691E:131a-2: de bzhin du mi la sogs pa'i sems can /
T02TD2691E:131a-3: rkang bzhi khyed cag bde legs shog / ces bya ba ni dud 'gro la sogs pa'i sems can rnams dang ste /
T02TD2691E:131a-4: sdug bsngal ni gcig gis gcig za ba'i sdug bsngal rnams te /
T02TD2691E:131a-5: de yang zhi bar byas shing yi dags rkang bzhi pa rnams kyi sdug bsngal yang zhi bar byas so //
T02TD2691E:131a-6: lam du zhugs rnams bde legs shog / ces bya ba ni gang zag 'di la gus par byed pa gang dang gang du phyin pa der bde zhing /
T02TD2691E:131a-8: phyir 'ong dag kyang bde legs shog / ces bya ba ni rang gi khyim du slebs nas kyang bde bar gyur cig / lus thams cad kyang nad dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:131a-9: mtshan mo bde legs nyin bde legs //
T02TD2691E:131a-10: nyi ma'i gung la bde legs shing //
T02TD2691E:131a-11: khyed cag kun du bde legs shog / ces bya ba ni nyal ba'i dus su yang rmi lam dge bar rmi zhing /
T02TD2691E:131a-12: mi dge ba rnams mi rmi /
T02TD2691E:131a-13: de bzhin du nyin mo yang dge ba'i sems su gnas shing /
T02TD2691E:131a-14: nyon mongs pa rnams mi skye ba'o //
T02TD2691E:131a-15: de bzhin du nyi ma phyed kyang yin no //
T02TD2691E:131a-16: de bzhin du nyin mtshan yang yin no ;
T02TD2691E:131a-17: ; de dag sdig par ma gyur cig / ces bya ba ni gang zag 'di la gnas pa ni skye ba bdun du tshe rabs dran zhing /
T02TD2691E:131a-18: 'di'i nus pas sdig pas mi gos pa'o //
T02TD2691E:131a-19: nyi ma thams cad dge ba yin //
T02TD2691E:131a-20: zhes bya ba ni rig sngags kyi nus pas mi dge ba las skyes kyang dge bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:131a-21: rgyu skar thams cad bzang po yin //
T02TD2691E:131a-22: zhes bya ba ni mi bzang ba ni skag dang bra nye'o //
T02TD2691E:131a-24: de las skyes pas kyang rig sngags kyi gzi brjid kyis /
T02TD2691E:131a-25: rgyu skar thams cad bzang po'o //
T02TD2691E:131a-26: sangs rgyas thams cad rdzu 'phrul che //
T02TD2691E:131a-27: zhes bya ba ni 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa de ltar yod pa'i gzi brjid kyi stobs kyi rdzu 'phrul gyis sems can thams cad bde ba'o //
T02TD2691E:131a-28: yang na nam mkha' bzhin du rdzu 'phrul gyis khyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:131a-29: dgra bcom thams cad zag pa zad //
T02TD2691E:131b-0: bdud bzhi bcom zhing bag chags kyi sgrib @131b pas ma gos pa ste /
T02TD2691E:131b-1: de bzhin du nyan thos kyi rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-2: bden pa'i tshig 'dis kun du bde legs su gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-3: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi bka' bde na pa dang /
T02TD2691E:131b-4: rig sngags gyi gzi brjid kyi stobs kyis /
T02TD2691E:131b-5: kun nas kun du bde legs su 'gyur ba'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-6: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa'i rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis zhes bya ba ni rnam par gzigs dang /
T02TD2691E:131b-11: 'od srungs la sogs pa'i 'das pa'i sangs rgyas gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed bye ba brgyad khri bzhi stong rnams kyis kyang /
T02TD2691E:131b-12: rjes su yi rang zhing gsungs pa /
T02TD2691E:131b-13: de bzhin du ma 'ongs pa rnams kyang byams pa la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-14: da ltar sh'akya thub pas gsungs shing rjes su yi rang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-15: de rnams kyi bka' nas gsungs te ;
T02TD2691E:131b-16: gzi brjid che zhing 'byung po rnams kyi gnyen po'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-17: bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni gang zag gus par byed pa sba ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-18: sdug bsngal thams cad las grol 'dod pas sba ba'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-19: yongs su bskyab pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-20: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sdug bsngal las skyob pa dang /
T02TD2691E:131b-21: yongs su gzung ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-24: yongs su bskyad pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-25: dge ba'i rtsa ba ci byas pa rgya cher 'phel ba'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-26: zhi ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-27: bar chad med cing dge ba'i rtsa ba ci byas pa gang yang zhi bar 'gyur zhing bsam pa 'grub pa'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-28: bde legs su 'gyur ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-29: tshe da ltar yang bde bas te /
T02TD2691E:131b-30: de bzhin du phyi ma yang bde ba'o //
T02TD2691E:131b-31: chad pa sbang ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-34: de la sogs pa'i chad pa thams cad spong ba yin no //
T02TD2691E:131b-35: mtshon cha sbang ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-36: dper na g-yul du zhugs pa'i dgra las rgyal bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:131b-37: dug gzhil ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:131b-38: dug 'thungs pa dang dug zos pa dang /
T02TD2691E:132a-0: phol mig dang g-yan pa dang me dpal la sogs pa'i dug @132a * //
T02TD2691E:132a-2: dug gsad pa dang zhes bya ba ni 'gro ba'i dug dang bsdad pa'i dug dang byed pa'i dug dang gsum bas la nas phyi nas dug nad mi ldang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-3: mtshams gcad pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132a-4: rig sngags 'dis phyogs mtshams steng 'og thams cad rig sngags kyi nus pas 'byung po rnams 'ong mi nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-5: sa bcing ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni sa g-yo ba'i sdug bsngal yang mi 'byung ste /
T02TD2691E:132a-6: gzhan yang ri dang khang pa la sogs pa yang mi rdib pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-7: lo brgya 'tsho bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132a-8: tshe thung ba ring bar byed cing nad thams cad dang bral nas bde bar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-9: ston brgya mthong bar shog shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132a-10: bza' ba dang btung ba phun sum tshogs shing /
T02TD2691E:132a-11: ma shi'i bar du g-yog dang ldan zhing bu tsha thams cad dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-12: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
T02TD2691E:132a-13: sems can gyi don la bka' stsal ba'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-14: gnod sbyin gang dag rgya mtsho la gnas pa'i gnod sbyin chen po dag dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132a-15: bsam gyis mi khyab pa rgya mtsho la gnas pa'i 'byung po la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-16: gang dag ri'i rgyal po ri rab dang zhes bya ba ni de bzhin du rgyal po bzhi la sogs pa gnod sbyin gyi rgyal po nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
T02TD2691E:132a-17: mthu chen sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
T02TD2691E:132a-18: gang dag ri'i rgyal po gzhan rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132a-19: ri'i rgyal po ma la ya dang /
T02TD2691E:132a-21: ri nag po la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-22: yang na stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi ri'i rgyal po ri rab dang bcas pa'i gnod sbyin 'byung po rnams so //
T02TD2691E:132a-23: 'brog rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132a-24: de la gnas pa'i gnod sbyin 'byung po rnams te /
T02TD2691E:132a-25: yang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams stong la gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-26: 'brog chen po dang zhes bya ba ni de bas kyang che bas na chen po ste /
T02TD2691E:132a-27: 'byung po rnams kyang de bas kyang che ba'o //
T02TD2691E:132a-28: klung rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132b-0: chu bo chen po nee ranydza ra la sogs pa de lta bu'i chu klung rnams la @132b yod pa'i gnod sbyin 'byung po rnams so //
T02TD2691E:132b-1: klu chen po rnams dang zhes bya ba ni phyi'i rgya mtsho chen po ste /
T02TD2691E:132b-2: de la gnas pa'i klu dang gnod sbyin dang sa bdag la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-3: sman ljongs rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132b-4: rdzing bu rnams yin te de la gnas pa'i 'byung po sa bdag dang sa srin la sogs pa stong gsum gyi stong chen po la gnas pa'i rdzing bu rnams so //
T02TD2691E:132b-5: sman ljongs chen po rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132b-6: de bas kyang che bas na chen po'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-7: 'bab chu rnams dang zhes bya ba ni ba lang spyod dang dbyangs ldan dang /
T02TD2691E:132b-8: sbrang rtsi'i blo gros la sogs pa'i 'bab chu la gnas pa'i gnod sbyin 'byung po rnams so //
T02TD2691E:132b-9: lteng ka rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132b-10: chu'i khron pa rnams te de la sogs pa chu mig la gnas pa'i sa srin dang sa bdag 'byung po gnod sbyin rnams gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-11: lu ma rnams dang zhes bya ba ni de'i lteng ka na gnas pa'i mtsho chen po ste /
T02TD2691E:132b-12: de klu las bab pas na lu ma'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-13: de la gnas pa'i 'byung po dang /
T02TD2691E:132b-15: ri'i phug rnams dang zhes bya ba ni stong bar du gnas pa'i ri rnams la rgyu ba'i yi dags rnams so //
T02TD2691E:132b-16: yang na gdong pa lta bar mi nus pa'i 'byung po rnams so //
T02TD2691E:132b-17: dur khrod rnams dang zhes bya ba ni dur khrod ni ngang pa dang /
T02TD2691E:132b-21: mes bsregs pa la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-22: de la gnas pa ni gnod sbyin dang 'byung po la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-23: dur khrod chen po rnams dang zhes bya ba ni bsil ba'i tshal dang /
T02TD2691E:132b-25: 'byung po ro langs la sogs pa'i dur khrod chen po rnams dang /
T02TD2691E:132b-26: de bas kyang che zhing 'byung po rnams che ba'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-27: bzhi mdo rnams dang zhes bya ba ni lam gyi rgya gram na gnas pa ste /
T02TD2691E:132b-29: grong rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:132b-30: de ni chu la gnas pa'i 'byung po rnams te /
T02TD2691E:132b-31: ma rungs pa thams cad byed pa /
T02TD2691E:132b-32: sems can la gnod cing grong la rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-33: grong khyer rnams dang zhes bya ba ni de bas kyang che ba ste /
T02TD2691E:132b-34: 'byung po yang de bas che ba'o //
T02TD2691E:132b-35: lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni 'brog gi 'brog gnas te /
T02TD2691E:133a-2: de na gnas pa'i gnod sbyin 'byung po rnams so //
T02TD2691E:133a-3: skyed mos tshal rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133a-4: pho dang mo rgyu ba'i gnas /
T02TD2691E:133a-5: de bzhin du 'byung po yang pho mo rgyu ba'i gzugs su byas nas rgyu bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133a-6: nags rnams dang zhes bya ba ni srin po yi dags rnams rgyu ba ste /
T02TD2691E:133a-7: de la gnas pa'i ma rungs pa rnams so //
T02TD2691E:133a-8: nags tshal rnams dang zhes bya ba ni chu'i bar na gnas pa ste /
T02TD2691E:133a-9: de'i nang du rgyu ba'i 'byung po rnams te /
T02TD2691E:133a-10: yang na rgya mtsho'i bar na gnas pa'i 'byung po rnams so //
T02TD2691E:133a-11: lam rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133a-12: 'gro 'dug byed pa la 'tshe bar byed cing ma rungs pa'i 'byung po ste /
T02TD2691E:133a-13: de bzhin du rtag tu rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:133a-14: lam gol ba dag na gnas pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133a-15: sems can lam log par 'khrid cing lam log par ston pa rnams so //
T02TD2691E:133a-16: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133a-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis kun dga' bo la yang nas yang du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133a-18: gnod sbyin gang dag lcang lo can gyi 'khor na gnas pa de dag gis kyang zhes bya ba ni gnod sbyin gyi ded dpon rnam thos sras kyi 'khor dang bcas pa de dag //
T02TD2691E:133a-19: pho brang de na gnas pa'i gnod sbyin 'khor bcas rnams so //
T02TD2691E:133a-20: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni gang zag dad pa skyes pa rnams dang /
T02TD2691E:133a-24: rjes su yi rang ba dang /
T02TD2691E:133a-27: de rnams la sogs pa yang dag par srung bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133a-28: lo brgya 'tsho bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133a-29: rig sngags 'di'i nus pas lo brgya lon par gyur kyang /
T02TD2691E:133a-30: gzhon nu'i tshul du bzhugs shing nad rnams thams cad dang bral ba'o //
T02TD2691E:133a-31: ston brgya mthong bar shog shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133a-32: dge ba'i dus su dge ba nus shing /
T02TD2691E:133a-33: de bzhin du za ba dang 'thung ba yang nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133a-34: rig sngags 'di yang sems can thams cad la thugs rje che zhing gzugs skur snang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:133a-35: gzugs sku de yang thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-0: zhal @133b gsum phyag bzhi pa sku mdog mthing nag tu bzhugs pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-1: g-yas dkar ba g-yon dmar ba /
T02TD2691E:133b-2: khro mo dbu skra ser po sbrul gyis bcings pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-5: yan lag sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-6: phyag g-yas na ral gri dang rdo rje 'dzin pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-7: g-yon sdigs mdzub dang zhags pa dril bu'o //
T02TD2691E:133b-10: zhabs kyis gnod sbyin pho mo mnan pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-11: padma'i steng du nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-13: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags 'di lta ste /
T02TD2691E:133b-14: 'byung po rnams kyi snying po ni ha re ni la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133b-15: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni sh'akya thub pas yang nas yang du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133b-16: shar phyogs na dri za'i rgyal po yul 'khor srung dri za thams cad kyi bdag po zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133b-17: ri rab kyi lcog shar phyogs na yod pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-20: phyag g-yas na 'khor lo bsnams pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-22: rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-24: sems can thams cad kyi don byed pa /
T02TD2691E:133b-25: 'jig rten gyi khams shar phyogs na gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133b-26: 'khor dri za stong phrag du ma yod pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133b-28: glu len zhing ni bro brdung ste //
T02TD2691E:133b-29: rgyan rnams la yang dga' bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:133b-30: brkam pa ma mchis mang bar smra /
T02TD2691E:133b-31: dgod par bgyid cing khro bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:133b-32: skom par 'gyur la mig dmar te //
T02TD2691E:133b-33: rtag tu rims kyis 'debs par bgyid ;
T02TD2691E:133b-34: ; mig kyang 'byed par mi bgyid de //
T02TD2691E:133b-35: rgyab kyis phyogs shing nyal bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:133b-36: 'khor 'bum phrag du ma de dag kyang sems can la de bzhin du gnod pa byas shing /
T02TD2691E:133b-37: rang gi mtshan nyid kyang de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:133b-38: dri za rnams la dbang byed du 'jug pa gnas te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:133b-39: de dang ldan pa dri za rnams la rgyal po chen po yul 'khor srung dbang du 'dus shing /
T02TD2691E:133b-40: gzhan sems can rnams la gnod par mi byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:133b-41: shar phyogs kyi rgyal po'am gdon rnams gnod par 'gyur na /
T02TD2691E:134a-0: tshes bcu bzhi 'am nya 'am brgyad la sogs pa la me tog gam spos @134a * //
T02TD2691E:134a-2: lha bshos sam mchod pa'i rtsas rang gis ci rigs pa bsogs la /
T02TD2691E:134a-3: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'am /
T02TD2691E:134a-4: shar phyogs kyi rgyal po yul 'khor srung la sogs pa /
T02TD2691E:134a-5: shar phyogs na gnas pa'i rgyal po dang gdon rnams mchod par bgyi'o //
T02TD2691E:134a-6: yang rol mo'i rdzas ni gdugs dang ba dan dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i rol mo'i rdzas so //
T02TD2691E:134a-8: bu ram dang bsres pa'i zho dang /
T02TD2691E:134a-11: 'bras las byas pa'i khur ba dang /
T02TD2691E:134a-12: de la sogs pa ci rigs pa bsogs la dri sna tshogs zhim pos mchod cing /
T02TD2691E:134a-13: me tog dkar po'i phreng ba dang /
T02TD2691E:134a-14: dog sa la me tog dkar po bkram la /
T02TD2691E:134a-15: yang dag par mchod par bgyi'o //
T02TD2691E:134a-16: gang shar phyogs srung zhing yongs su skyob par byed pa de yang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134a-17: sa dang po'i byang chub sems dpa' sems can thams cad kyi don byed pa de lta bu'i yul 'khor srung gi rgyal po /
T02TD2691E:134a-18: shar phyogs kyi sems can rnams skyong ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134a-19: bu dang bcas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134a-20: rgyal po chen po bzhi dang 'khor rnams kyi'o //
T02TD2691E:134a-28: 'khor dang bcas pas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134a-29: de dag rnams kyis sems can gyi don byas shing rgyal po dang /
T02TD2691E:134a-30: 'khor rnams kyi tsha bo la sogs pa'i 'bum phrag du mar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:134a-31: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis bdag la srung ba shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134a-32: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo ni /
T02TD2691E:134a-36: g-yon sdigs mdzub dang rma bya'i sgro bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:134a-37: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2691E:134a-39: rgyan thams cad rin po ches brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:134a-40: lo bcu gnyis ma'i cha byad can /
T02TD2691E:134a-41: zhi bar bzhugs shing padma'i steng na zla ba'i gang na /
T02TD2691E:134a-43: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin can /
T02TD2691E:134b-0: @134b mtshon byed ni shes rab ste /
T02TD2691E:134b-1: mtshon pa ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo bdag nyid do //
T02TD2691E:134b-2: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi gzugs kyi phung po sa'i khams mig gi skye mched do //
T02TD2691E:134b-3: de lta bu'i rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gang zag bdag gis 'chang bar 'gyur na /
T02TD2691E:134b-4: yang dag par srung zhing sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-5: sba ba dang zhes bya ba ni ma rungs pa rnams kyis glags tshol ba la sba ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-6: yongs su bskyab pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134b-7: nad thams cad dang ma rungs pa rnams kyis bzung ba las bskyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-8: yongs su gzung ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134b-9: ma rig pa'i sems can rnams kyis gzung bar 'dod pa /
T02TD2691E:134b-10: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid kyis bzung nas glags mi rnyed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-11: yongs su bskyang ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134b-12: rig sngags kyi gzi brjid kyis gang gi 'jigs pa dang sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral zhing 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral ba ste /
T02TD2691E:134b-13: rgya chen bskyang bas na yongs su bskyang ba dang /
T02TD2691E:134b-14: zhi ba dang bde legs su 'gyur ba dang zhes bya ba ni zhi ba ni sdug bsngal thams cad zhi ba ste /
T02TD2691E:134b-15: de nye bar bzhag pas na bde ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-16: bde legs su 'gyur ba dang zhes bya ba ni bde ba phun sum tshogs shing sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral zhing nam skyes pa'i dus su yang bde ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-17: chad pa spang ba dang zhes bya ba ni ma rungs pa'i gdon gyis chad pa gcod par 'dod pa la /
T02TD2691E:134b-18: de'i gzi brjid kyis sbrang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-19: mtshon cha sbang ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134b-20: gzhan rnams kyis mtshon btab nas /
T02TD2691E:134b-21: mi bde ba dang mi phog pa'i phyir na spang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-22: dug gzhil ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134b-28: me dbal la sogs pa mdze rigs bco brgyad sel ba'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-29: dug gsad pa dang zhes bya ba ni de rnams mi ldang bar bya ba'i phyir na gsad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:134b-30: mtshams gcad pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:134b-31: glags tshol ba rnams kyis glags mi rnyed de /
T02TD2691E:134b-32: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags gar bzhag pa'i sar /
T02TD2691E:134b-33: 'byung po rnams kyis 'ong mi nus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-0: sa bcing ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni rig sngags kyis sa @135a * //
T02TD2691E:135a-1: la reg nas sa bcing bar gyur na rdo rje'i sa gzhi dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-2: lo brgya mtsho bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-3: nad thams cad dang bral zhing bde bar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-4: ston brgya mthong bar shog shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-5: phun sum tshogs shing bde bar gnas pa'o//
T02TD2691E:135a-6: tadya th'a zhes bya ba ni 'di lta ste 'og tu blta'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-7: dri za'i snying po rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-8: su ru su ru su ru la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-9: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni dge slong sa ri dang sems can rnams la bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-10: lho phyogs na grul bum gyi rgyal po 'phags skyes po zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-11: ri rab kyi lho phyogs na gnas pa 'jig rten lho phyogs skyong ba /
T02TD2691E:135a-12: sems can thams cad kyi don byed pa /
T02TD2691E:135a-14: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing ga / g-yas dbyug to //
T02TD2691E:135a-15: g-yon rin po che bsnams pa /
T02TD2691E:135a-16: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:135a-20: grul bum thams cad kyi bdag po 'khor grul bum stong phrag du ma yod pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-21: grul bu ma yi dags kyi gdon rnams kyi bdag po ste /
T02TD2691E:135a-22: de bzhin du ma mo rnams kyang yin no //
T02TD2691E:135a-23: de rnams kyis btab pa'i mtshan ma ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-25: g-yeng bas btab cing lta bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:135a-26: bzhin yang dmar por gda' bar 'gyur /
T02TD2691E:135a-27: bskums nas sa la nyal bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:135a-28: kha dog ngan cing lus kyang skem //
T02TD2691E:135a-29: skra dang sen mo ring ba ste //
T02TD2691E:135a-30: dri ma can la dri mi bda' //
T02TD2691E:135a-31: brdzun dang kyal ka smra bar bgyid //
T02TD2691E:135a-32: grum bum gyi gdon 'bum phrag du ma gnas pa ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-33: sems can rnams la gnod par bgyid cing rgyal po'i 'khor du gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-34: grul bum rnams la dbang byed du 'jug pa'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135a-35: grul bum gyi gdon de rnams dbang du sdud cing /
T02TD2691E:135a-36: sems can rnams la 'tshe bar mi byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135a-37: de rnams kyi mchod pa'i rdzas ni gong dang mthun no //
T02TD2691E:135a-38: tshes grangs yang gong dang mthun no //
T02TD2691E:135a-39: gtor ma'i rdzas la khrag gam chang ngam sha'am nya'am sgog pa'am la phug gam /
T02TD2691E:135b-0: sran chan nam @135b khur ba'am bu ram gyi thug pa'am /
T02TD2691E:135b-1: khrag gi gtor ma me tog ser po'i phreng ba dang /
T02TD2691E:135b-2: dog sa la me tog bkram la /
T02TD2691E:135b-3: lho phyogs na gnas pa'i rgyal po rnams mchod par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-4: gang lho phyogs srung zhing yongs su skyong bar byed cing zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135b-5: grul bum gyi rgyal po 'phags skyes po ri rab kyi lho phyogs yongs su srung zhing /
T02TD2691E:135b-6: 'jig rten kyi khams rnams la srung bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-15: 'khor dang bcas pas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135b-16: rgyal po chen po 'phags skyes po dang /
T02TD2691E:135b-18: de rnams kyi bu dang tsha bo la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-19: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135b-20: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo ni thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-21: ye shes mnyam pa nyid dang ldan pa tshor ba'i phung po'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-22: rin chen gyi rigs chu'i khams sna'i skye mched ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa sku mdog ser po /
T02TD2691E:135b-23: phyag g-yas na ral gri / g-yon na rma bya'i sgro bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-24: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2691E:135b-25: rgyan thams cad rin po ches brgyan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-26: spyan gsum pa zhabs phyed krung du bzhugs pa /
T02TD2691E:135b-27: nyi ma'i gdan dang 'od dang ldan pa /
T02TD2691E:135b-28: de'i 'og tu padma'i gdan la khro mor bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-29: gang zag gang zhig 'di la gus par gyur na /
T02TD2691E:135b-30: rgyal po bzhi dang 'khor rnams kyis kyang de la srung zhing skyob par byed do //
T02TD2691E:135b-31: sba ba dang zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni sngar bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-32: ta dya th'a zhes bya ba ni 'di lta ste 'og tu bltas te /
T02TD2691E:135b-33: 'og tu lta ba ni gang zhe na /
T02TD2691E:135b-34: grul bum gyi gdon gyi snying po rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni /
T02TD2691E:135b-35: be lu ke la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-36: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis kun dga' bo la bka' stsal ba'o //
T02TD2691E:135b-37: nub phyogs na klu'i rgyal po mig mi bzang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:135b-38: ri rab kyi rtse mo'i nub phyogs kyi lcog la bzhugs te /
T02TD2691E:135b-39: nub phyogs kyi 'jig rten skyong ba /
T02TD2691E:136a-1: kyi bdag po sa dang po thob pa /
T02TD2691E:136a-2: byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pa rnams so //
T02TD2691E:136a-5: g-yas na sprul gyi zhags pa /
T02TD2691E:136a-7: rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:136a-9: cung zad khro bor bzhugs so //
T02TD2691E:136a-10: klu thams cad kyi bdag po 'khor 'bum phrag du ma yod pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:136a-11: rgyal po spyan mi bzang yang klu dangs [?] srin sa bdag rnams yin te /
T02TD2691E:136a-12: de rnams kyis btab pa'i mtshan ma ni /
T02TD2691E:136a-13: skyigs bus btab cing dbugs kyang 'byin //
T02TD2691E:136a-14: de bzhin dbugs kyang grang bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:136a-15: rdul zhing kha chu dbu bar 'byung //
T02TD2691E:136a-16: phyi phyir gnyid kyis log par 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:136a-17: kha dog ldan zhing dpa' ba ste /
T02TD2691E:136a-19: sen mo dag kyang ston par 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:136a-20: dog sar mchis shing du bar byed //
T02TD2691E:136a-21: de bzhin du sems can rnams la mtshan ma btab nas /
T02TD2691E:136a-22: rang gi mtshan ma yang de dang 'dra ba'o //
T02TD2691E:136a-23: klu rnams la dbang byed du 'jug pa gnas te /
T02TD2691E:136a-24: de rnams dbang du 'dus shing 'jig rten nub phyogs song ba de rnams mchod pa'i rdzas gong dang mthun te /
T02TD2691E:136a-25: tshes grangs kyang gong dang mthun no //
T02TD2691E:136a-26: gtor ma'i rdzas ni mngar gsum dang dkar gsum 'o thug dang gro chan dang gro'i khur ba 'o ma las byas pa'i gtor ma me tog dmar po'i phreng ba me tog sil ma dog sa la bkram la /
T02TD2691E:136a-27: klu sman la sogs pas mchod par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:136a-28: gang nub phyogs skyong zhing yongs su srung bar byed pa de yang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:136a-29: rgyal po spyan mi bzang des kyang ri rab kyi nub phyogs na yongs su skyong zhing sems can rnams la 'tshe bar mi byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:136a-30: bu dang bcas pa la sogs pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:136a-31: rgyal po chen po spyan mi bzang gi bu la sogs pa dang /
T02TD2691E:136a-32: 'khor rnams kyi bu la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:136a-33: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo ni zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD2691E:136a-36: g-yon rma bya'i sgro bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:136a-37: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2691E:136b-1: rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /

T02TD2691E:136b-14: tadya th'a zhes bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
T02TD2691E:136b-17: klu rnams kyi snying po rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni /
T02TD2691E:136b-18: be du ri be du ri zhes bya ba la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:136b-19: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /

T02TD2691E:136b-22: byang phyogs kyi rgyal po lus ngan po yin te /
T02TD2691E:136b-23: ri rab kyi rtse mo'i byang phyogs kyi lcog la bzhugs te /

T02TD2691E:136b-26: g-yon na ne'u le'i rkyal pa bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:136b-27: rgyan thams cad rin po ches brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:136b-29: ; gsus pa che zhing stong chung ba khro bor bzhugs pa'o //

T02TD2691E:136b-36: yang na shin tu khro bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:136b-37: rtag tu gyen du lta bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:136b-38: skar ma dag la snyegs par bgyid //
T02TD2691E:136b-39: nub mo shin tu dga' bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:136b-41: gnod sbyin gyi rang bzhin yang de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:136b-42: gnod sbyin rnams la dbang byed du 'jug pa gnas te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:136b-43: gnod sbyin 'bum phrag du ma gnas pa rnams la mnga' mdzad /
T02TD2691E:137a-0: gang byang phyogs srung zhing yongs su @137a * //

T02TD2691E:137a-7: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di yang zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD2691E:137a-8: sku mdog ljang gu phyag g-yas na ral gri / g-yon na rma bya'i sgro bsnams pa'o//
T02TD2691E:137a-9: las kyi rigs bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes /
T02TD2691E:137a-10: 'du byed kyi phung po rlung gi khams yid kyi skye mched ye shes lnga'i ngo bo nyid /

T02TD2691E:137a-18: srung bar 'gyur zhing ma shi bar bde bar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:137a-19: sba ba la sogs pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:137a-21: tadya th'a zhes bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
T02TD2691E:137a-22: gang lta zhe na 'og tu blta ba ni gnod sbyin gyi snying po rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni /
T02TD2691E:137a-23: soo ri soo ri la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:137a-24: shar phyogs na ni yul 'khor srung //

T02TD2691E:137a-27: lho phyogs na ni 'phags skyes po //

T02TD2691E:137a-32: zhes bya ba ni klu'i 'bum phrag du ma dang bcas shing /
T02TD2691E:137a-34: byang phyogs na ni lus ngan po //
T02TD2691E:137a-35: zhes bya ba ni gnod sbyin gyi 'khor 'bum phrag du ma dang bcas nas byang phyogs srung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:137a-36: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la gus par byed cing srung ba btags na /
T02TD2691E:137a-37: rgyal po chen po bzhi 'khor dang bcas nas srung ba da nga sba ba la sogs pa byed par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:137b-0: @137b rgyal po chen po 'di bzhi dag //
T02TD2691E:137b-1: ces bya ba ni 'khor rgyal po chen po bzhis byas shing /
T02TD2691E:137b-2: rig sngags rgyal mo gtso bor byas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:137b-3: dogs sa gzhi bzang po la //
T02TD2691E:137b-4: me long dbyibs bzhin mkhas pas byas //
T02TD2691E:137b-5: de steng tshon lngas bri ba la //
T02TD2691E:137b-6: mdzes par byas nas yang dag bri //
T02TD2691E:137b-7: gru bzhi sgo bzhi tva ran bzhi //
T02TD2691E:137b-8: dbus su sna tshogs padma la //
T02TD2691E:137b-9: rig sngags rgyal mo yang dag bzhugs //
T02TD2691E:137b-11: rgal po bzhi yang bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:137b-12: de bzhin gser gyi padma la //
T02TD2691E:137b-13: mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi yang dgod //
T02TD2691E:137b-14: sgo bzhi dang ni zur rnams la //
T02TD2691E:137b-15: phyogs skyong bcu yang dgod par bya //
T02TD2691E:137b-16: rdo rje ra ba'i phyi rim la //
T02TD2691E:137b-17: rgyal chen bzhi yi 'khor rnams dgod //
T02TD2691E:137b-18: de bzhin 'byung po la sogs dang //
T02TD2691E:137b-19: mkhas pas yang dag bri bar bya //
T02TD2691E:137b-20: rgyal po bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi bya thab so //
T02TD2691E:137b-21: de nas bum pa'i bya thabs ni //
T02TD2691E:137b-22: mtshan ma legs pa mgrin pa ring //
T02TD2691E:137b-23: nag po ra ri spangs pa dang //
T02TD2691E:137b-24: mchu 'phyang lto ba che ba dang //
T02TD2691E:137b-25: dar ram ras sam gang yang rung //
T02TD2691E:137b-26: mgrin pa yangs par bcing bar bya //
T02TD2691E:137b-27: rin chen lnga dang 'bru lnga dang //
T02TD2691E:137b-28: sman lnga dri lnga snying po lnga //
T02TD2691E:137b-29: chu gtsang gis ni legs par dgang //
T02TD2691E:137b-30: gdugs dang ba dan rgyal mtshan dang //
T02TD2691E:137b-31: lo ma lnga dang ldan pa dang //
T02TD2691E:137b-32: bkra shis brgyad dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD2691E:137b-33: de rnams kyis ni brgyan nas ni //
T02TD2691E:137b-34: dkyil 'khor dbus su yang dag gzhag / snying po'am nye ba'i snying po'am //
T02TD2691E:137b-35: de'i sngags kyis bum pa lhag par byed pa'i cho ga byas la /
T02TD2691E:137b-37: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa mang phyis bshad pa bzhin du bya'o //
T02TD2691E:137b-38: rgyal po chen po bzhi'i 'khor gyis /
T02TD2691E:137b-39: nad kyis btab pa de sngar bshad pa'i snying po'i sngags kyis bsrung bar bya'o //
T02TD2691E:137b-40: de bzhin du srung ba byas na /
T02TD2691E:137b-41: rgyal po chen po bzhis kyang 'jig rten skyong zhing nad pa yang skyong bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:137b-42: 'jig rten skyong ba grags dang ldan //
T02TD2691E:137b-43: zhes bya ba gling bzhi'i ri rab dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams na grags pa'o //
T02TD2691E:137b-44: phyogs bzhi dag ni skyong bar byed //
T02TD2691E:138a-0: ces bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgya @138a * //
T02TD2691E:138a-1: rgyas rnams kyi chos skyong ba byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang pho thob nas sems can rnams kyi don mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-2: sde bo che la stobs bo che //
T02TD2691E:138a-3: zhes bya ba ni dri za dang grul bum dang /
T02TD2691E:138a-6: de rnams kyi ded dpon te /
T02TD2691E:138a-7: de rnams la che bar mdzad cing 'jig rten la grags pa'i stobs dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-8: pha rol dgra rnams rab tu 'joms //
T02TD2691E:138a-9: zhes bya ba ni lha dang lha ma yin gyi yul la pha rol 'dul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-10: gzhan gyis mi thub thub par dka' //
T02TD2691E:138a-11: zhes bya ba ni gzhan 'jig rten gyi lha rnams kyis mi thub pa stobs che ba dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-13: zhes bya ba ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams skad cig mas khyab cing sems can rnams kyi don mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-15: kha dog ldan zhing grags dang ldan //
T02TD2691E:138a-16: zhes bya ba ni so so rang gi kha dog dang ldan zhing /
T02TD2691E:138a-17: de bzhin grags pa yang yin no //
T02TD2691E:138a-18: rdzu 'phrul che zhing lha min dang //
T02TD2691E:138a-19: lha yi yul yang myong bar byed //
T02TD2691E:138a-20: ces bya ba ni lha dang lha ma yin gyi spyod pa la yang rtsod par nus shing /
T02TD2691E:138a-21: pha rol gyi dgra rnams 'dul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-22: de dag gis kyang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni rgyal po chen po bzhi 'khor bcas dang /
T02TD2691E:138a-23: gang zag bdag la srung bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-24: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di /
T02TD2691E:138a-25: mtshon bya ni shes rab ste mtshon byed ni thabs so //
T02TD2691E:138a-27: rin po che'i rigs mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
T02TD2691E:138a-28: tshor ba'i phung po chu'i khams /
T02TD2691E:138a-29: sna'i skye mched ye shes lnga'i ngo bo nyid /
T02TD2691E:138a-32: g-yas mthing ga / g-yon dmar ba zhal dang po sgeg pa /
T02TD2691E:138a-35: zhal re re la spyan gsum dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-37: dbu la rin po che'i rdo rjes brgyan pa /
T02TD2691E:138a-38: rgyan thams cad rin po ches brgyan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-39: phyag g-yas dang po ral gri //
T02TD2691E:138a-40: 'og ma na rdo rje rin po che /
T02TD2691E:138a-42: 'og ma na rma bya'i sgro tha ma gnyis na mda' gzhu 'gengs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138a-43: zhabs rdo rje skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
T02TD2691E:138b-0: sna tshogs @138b padma'i steng du zla ba'i gdan /
T02TD2691E:138b-1: nyi ma bdun dang ldan pa'i 'od mnga' ba /
T02TD2691E:138b-2: bcu drug lon pa'i cha byad can thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa gang zag dag gis gus par byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-3: sba ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-4: sdug bsngal thams cad sba ba'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-5: yongs su bskyab pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-6: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las bskyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-7: yongs su gzung ba dang zhes bya ba ni mi dge bcu spangs nas dge ba bcu la gzud pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-8: yongs su bskyang ba dang zhes bya ba ni ma rig pa bcom nas yon tan skyong ba'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-9: zhi ba dang bde legs su 'gyur ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-10: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal zhi bar 'gyur te /
T02TD2691E:138b-11: yang dag pa'i don thob nas mtho ris kyi ngo bo nyid thob pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-12: chad pa spang ba dang zhes bya ba ni bdud bzhi rnams kyi chad pa spangs nas ye shes shar ba'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-13: mtshon cha spang ba dang zhes bya ba ni dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal mtshon cha spang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-14: dug gzhil ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-15: dug lnga shar ba la des bsil bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-16: dug gsang ba dang zhes bya ba ni ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gyis dug lnga gsad pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-17: mtshams gcad pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-18: ma rig pa'i ngo bo bsad nas /
T02TD2691E:138b-19: ye shes kyi ngo bo la 'jug pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-20: sa bcing bgyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-21: sdig pa'i sems dang ldan pa rnams dge ba la 'jug pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-22: lo brgya 'tsho bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-23: rig sngags 'di'i gzi brjid kyis nad med cing shi ba'i dus kyis mi gos ba'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-24: ston brgya mthong bar shog shig ces bya ba ni /

T02TD2691E:138b-27: 'di lta ste gang lta zhe na rig sngags kyi gsang sngags bsam gyis mi khyab pa blta'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-28: rig sngags kyi gsang sngags ni /
T02TD2691E:138b-29: ae le me le la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:138b-30: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i rgyal po bzhi'i cho ga'i gnas skabs te brgyad pa'o /

T02TD2691E:139a-0: khyod kyis gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po rnams kyi mang [*ming?] @139a * //
