T02TD2691E:217a-1: mdog dud ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis ba /
T02TD2691E:217a-2: phyag g-yas na ral gri bsnams pa /
T02TD2691E:217a-3: g-yon na zhags pa bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217a-4: khams lnga ka la gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217a-5: gza' de rnams kyi dus su rig pa slob par 'dod na bzang ngan gyi khyad par brtags la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:217a-6: chos dang slob ma 'dzin pa bo //
T02TD2691E:217a-7: slob dpon 'dzin pa de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:217a-8: gza' chen phur bu'i dus su ni /
T02TD2691E:217a-9: dbu 'dzugs de ni bzang ba yin //
T02TD2691E:217a-10: de bzhin rig pa gzhan la yang //
T02TD2691E:217a-11: de yi dus su bzang bar bshad //
T02TD2691E:217a-12: skra mdud gos ni gsar ba'am //
T02TD2691E:217a-13: zas dang gsar pa gang byed pa //
T02TD2691E:217a-14: de yi dus su bzang bar bshad //
T02TD2691E:217a-16: de bzhin gos bzo byed pa dang //
T02TD2691E:217a-17: rta dang glang po sogs pa'i nor //
T02TD2691E:217a-18: de yi dus su phyir mi gtang //
T02TD2691E:217a-19: gal te btang bar gyur na ni //
T02TD2691E:217a-21: nyi ma spen ba'i gza' gnyis la //
T02TD2691E:217a-23: dmag dang 'khrug pa gang byed pa //
T02TD2691E:217a-24: de yi dus su 'dren pa na //
T02TD2691E:217a-25: rab tu yang dag bshad par bya //
T02TD2691E:217a-26: skra dang sen mo gos la sogs //
T02TD2691E:217a-27: de yi dus su byas na ni //
T02TD2691E:217a-28: nad dang rims la sogs pa 'byung //
T02TD2691E:217a-29: shi ba'i dus la bab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217a-30: lam 'gro dbang bskur la sogs dang //
T02TD2691E:217a-31: nyi ma'i dus su bzang bar bshad //
T02TD2691E:217a-32: sben pa'i dus su de byas na //
T02TD2691E:217a-33: shin tu ngan par de bshad do //
T02TD2691E:217a-34: gal te de dus byas na ni //
T02TD2691E:217a-36: mig dmar dang ni lag ba la //
T02TD2691E:217a-37: rig pa gang gi mgo 'dzugs pa //
T02TD2691E:217a-38: slob ma slob dpon 'brel byed pa //
T02TD2691E:217a-39: lam 'gro nye tshong byed ba dang //
T02TD2691E:217a-40: dbang bskur la sogs gang byed pa //
T02TD2691E:217a-42: ngan pa'i las ni gang byed pa //
T02TD2691E:217a-43: de yi dus su bzang bar 'gyur //
T02TD2691E:217a-44: zla ba dang ni ba ba sangs //
T02TD2691E:217a-45: de dus rig pa slobs gyur na //
T02TD2691E:217a-46: go ba ma rnyed gti mug nas //
T02TD2691E:217a-47: las ni gang dag byed pa na //
T02TD2691E:217a-49: de ltar gza' bdun po'i dus su khrus la sogs pa byed pa ni gza' lag pa la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:217a-50: gos gsar ba 'drub pa dang gcod pa ni /
T02TD2691E:217a-51: zla ba dang ba ba sangs la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-0: chos la sogs pa'i rig pa @217b ni ;
T02TD2691E:217b-4: bza' gsar pa byed pa ni /
T02TD2691E:217b-5: nyi ma dang spen pa la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-6: nyi ma las skyes pa'i bu ni shin tu grags pa mis mi thub pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-7: zla ba las skyes pa'i bu ni 'jam zhing dbang po zhen pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-8: mig dmar las skyes pa'i bu ni sdig la dga' zhing drag por skyes pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-9: pa ba sangs las skyes pa ni /
T02TD2691E:217b-10: ser sna che zhing 'dod chags la dga' ba'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-11: phur bu las skyes pa ni shin tu grags la yon tan ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-12: spen pa las skyes pa ni 'bring du shes par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-13: gza' lag pa las skyes pa ni ltogs par 'gyur zhing sdig ba la dga' ba'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-15: de rnams ni gza' brtag ba'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-16: gza'i la nye brtag pa ni /
T02TD2691E:217b-17: nyi ma'i dus su ni mdze pho dang nad 'gos pa'i mi dang 'phrad bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:217b-18: yang na btsun ba dang phrad do //
T02TD2691E:217b-19: zla ba'i dus su bud med rgan mo gos nag po gon ba dang phrad do //
T02TD2691E:217b-20: mig dmar gyi dus su ni sngags pa gos dmar po gon ba'am /
T02TD2691E:217b-21: bud med sham bu dmar po btags pa dang phrad do //
T02TD2691E:217b-22: pa ba sangs kyi dus su ni /
T02TD2691E:217b-23: btsun pa 'am bud med gos ser po gon pa dang phrad do //
T02TD2691E:217b-25: mda' thogs pa'i mi ral ba can dang phrad do //
T02TD2691E:217b-28: lag pa'i dus su rkang pa 'thed ba'am /
T02TD2691E:217b-29: lag pa zha ba dang phrad do //
T02TD2691E:217b-30: gza' bdun gyi la nye brtag pa'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-31: gza' r'a hu la dang du ba mjug rings ni /
T02TD2691E:217b-32: khams lnga'i rang bzhin gzhan gyis mi thub pa drag shul che ba'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-33: dpyid zlar ba'i chos bzhi la srod la shar nas nub tu rgyu //
T02TD2691E:217b-34: chos brgyad la srod yol nas lho nub mtshams nas byang shar mtshams su rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-35: tshes bcu gnyis la byang nas lhor rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-36: bcu drug la nyi ma phyed na shar lho mtshams nas byang shar mtshams su rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-37: nyi shu tham pa la nub nas shar du nam phyed na rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-38: nyi shu bzhi la tho rangs ka shar lho nas nub byang du rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:217b-39: nyi shu brgyad la nyi ma mdung gang na byang nas lhor rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-0: gnam stong la nyi ma nub @218a * //
T02TD2691E:218a-1: nas lho nub mtshams nas byang shar mtshams su rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-2: dpyid zla 'bring pa'i tshes bzhi la srod la nub nas shar du rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-3: de bzhin du zla ba lhag ma bcu po la yang spel mar shes par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-4: las dang bya ba ci byed kyang gza' rgyu ba dang /
T02TD2691E:218a-5: gdong thug tu mi bya bar kho dang 'grogs la bya'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-6: zla ba gang yang rung ba la /
T02TD2691E:218a-8: zla ba gang yang rung ba'i tshes gcig la ni snga dro chu tshod lnga la kho gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-9: tshes bdun la chu tshod bcu tham pa /
T02TD2691E:218a-10: nyin phyed nas kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-11: tshes brgyad la nyi ma mdung gang la chu tshod bzhi kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-12: tshes bcu bzhi la nyi ma dros nas chu tshod nyi shu kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-13: tshes bco lnga la nyi ma phyed nas chu tshod drug kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-14: tshes bcu drug la srod 'khor nas chu tshod bdun la kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-15: nyi shu gnyis la nam phyed nas chu tshod gsum kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-16: nyi shu gsum la nam phyed nas chu tshod gsum 'das nas chu tshod lnga kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-17: nyi shu dgu la byang drang po nas chu tshod brgyad kho'i dus so //
T02TD2691E:218a-18: gnam stong la nyi ma phyed nas nam phyed du rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-19: de'i dus su las dang bya ba ci byed kyang /
T02TD2691E:218a-21: de'i phyir na las bya ba ci yang mi bya'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-22: hal khyi na lnga yod do //
T02TD2691E:218a-23: hal khyi nag po dang dkar po dang /
T02TD2691E:218a-26: ljang gu dang lnga bo de zla ba dkar po dang nag po /
T02TD2691E:218a-27: stod smad du spel nas rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:218a-29: mjug na yang gdong pa yod pa /
T02TD2691E:218a-30: kha nas me 'bar ba de dang 'phrad par gyur na gang gis kyang mi thub cing sdug bsngal thams cad 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:218a-31: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni /
T02TD2691E:218a-32: de ltar phyogs na bdun bdun no //
T02TD2691E:218a-38: nab so lcags kyi khams so //
T02TD2691E:218a-41: bdun bo de dag ni shar phyogs na gnas so //
T02TD2691E:218a-45: me bzhi ni lcags kyi khams /
T02TD2691E:218a-49: de dag bdun po ni lho na gnas so //
T02TD2691E:218b-6: bdun bo de dag ni nub kyi phyogs na gnas sa //
T02TD2691E:218b-13: bra nye shing gi khams so //
T02TD2691E:218b-14: bdun po de dag ni byang gi phyogs na gnas so //
T02TD2691E:218b-15: skar ma gza' bdun de dag de bzhin te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:218b-16: gza' de yang bdun bzhir rgyu ste /
T02TD2691E:218b-18: bzang ba dang ngan par ston pa'o //
T02TD2691E:218b-19: rdzu 'phrul che zhing dka' thub che //
T02TD2691E:218b-21: gling bzhi ri rab dang bcas par bskor ba'o //
T02TD2691E:218b-22: 'jig rten gyi mi rnams la bzang ba dang ngan par ston pa ste /
T02TD2691E:218b-23: de'i dus tshod shes par gyur na /
T02TD2691E:218b-26: nyi ma dang ni zla ba dang //
T02TD2691E:218b-27: sum cu rtsa gsum tshang bdag / ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:218b-28: zla ba re re la gza' dgu dang /
T02TD2691E:218b-29: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:218b-30: nyi ma dang zla ba mig dmar dang /
T02TD2691E:218b-32: phur bu spen pa lag pa /
T02TD2691E:218b-33: r'a hu la du ba mjug rings /
T02TD2691E:218b-34: shar gyi phyogs nas go rims bzhin du rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:218b-35: skar ma rnams kyang de bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:218b-36: r'a hu la dang du ba mjug rings ni /
T02TD2691E:218b-38: gzhan gyi tshes grangs la gza' gnyis po thod rgal du rgyu'o //
T02TD2691E:218b-39: 'char ba dang ni nub pa ni //
T02TD2691E:218b-41: phyi mngon pa'i dbang du bshad ba dang /
T02TD2691E:218b-42: nang gas bsngags kyi dbang du bshad pa ni /
T02TD2691E:218b-43: shar ba ni 'jig rten khams kyi mi rnams /
T02TD2691E:218b-44: skyes pa la ni nyi ma shar ba zhes bya'o //
T02TD2691E:218b-45: dper na 'jig rten du nyi ma shar ba bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:218b-46: nub pa ni 'jig rten gyi khams kyi mi rgas nas shi ba la nub pa zhes bya'o /
T02TD2691E:218b-47: 'khor lo mtshon cha bzhin du rgyu //
T02TD2691E:218b-49: rgyu lugs rnam pa gsum yod de /
T02TD2691E:218b-50: 'khor lo bzhin du rgyu ba dang /
T02TD2691E:218b-51: mtshon cha bzhin du rgyu ba dang /
T02TD2691E:218b-52: dbyu gu'i gros kyis rgyu ba gsum yod pa las /
T02TD2691E:218b-53: 'khor lo bzhin du rgyu ba ni /
T02TD2691E:218b-54: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi ri rab la /
T02TD2691E:219a-2: mtshon cha bzhin du rgyu ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219a-3: nyi ma'i 'gros te tha skar rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:219a-4: dbyu gu'i 'gros ni chu tshod la brtsis te /
T02TD2691E:219a-5: gcig por nas gcig len pa dbyu gu'i 'gros so //
T02TD2691E:219a-6: de bzhin du gza' rnams kyang rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:219a-7: da ni rnal 'byor gyi dbang du byas na sna bug g-yas g-yon gnyis na rgyu ba'i dbugs ni /
T02TD2691E:219a-8: nyin mo dang nub mo rgyu ba ni rgyu skar bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:219a-9: nyin zhag gcig la chu tshod drug cu yod pa la /
T02TD2691E:219a-10: dbugs kyang de bzhin du rgyu ba'o //
T02TD2691E:219a-13: zla ba ni tshes stod la 'phel te /
T02TD2691E:219a-15: dbugs kyang phyir 'gro ba ni ring ste /
T02TD2691E:219a-16: nang du rngub pa ni thung ste /
T02TD2691E:219a-17: de bzhin du 'jig rten gyi khams na gnas pa'i sems can rnams la yang zad pa dang 'phel bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:219a-18: de bas na 'jig rten gyi khams kyi sems can rnams la yang /
T02TD2691E:219a-20: yang na 'jig rten gyi khams kyi mi rnams nor 'phel ba dang /
T02TD2691E:219a-22: zla ba ji bzhin du 'jig rten gyi khams kyang 'phel 'grib byed do //
T02TD2691E:219a-23: gzi brjid rdzu 'phrul chen po dag / ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219a-24: rdzu 'phrul ni gling bzhi dang ri rab la rgyu ba ste /
T02TD2691E:219a-25: gzhan rnams kyang zil gyis gnon pa'o //
T02TD2691E:219a-26: de bzhin du 'jig rten gyi sgyu ma bzhin du snang bas na /
T02TD2691E:219a-27: 'jig rten gyi khams na gzi brjid che zhing rdzu 'phrul che ba'o //
T02TD2691E:219a-28: rab tu dang ba'i sems kyis su //
T02TD2691E:219a-29: rig sngags rjes su yi rang byos //
T02TD2691E:219a-31: 'jig rten khams na gnas pa'i gza' dang rgyu skar rnams kyis kyang /
T02TD2691E:219a-32: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo la gus pa'i sems kyis rjes su yi rang bas te /
T02TD2691E:219a-33: rig sngags kyi bka' las mi 'da' ba'o //
T02TD2691E:219a-34: de dag gis kyang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis /
T02TD2691E:219a-35: bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219a-36: nam mkha' bzhin du 'jig rten gyi khams la khyab ste /
T02TD2691E:219a-37: de yang bsam gyis mi khyab pa dag gis brjod du mi btub pa /
T02TD2691E:219a-38: rgya cher sems can rnams kyi don byed pa'o//
T02TD2691E:219b-0: @219b de lta bu'i rig sngags gang zag gang gis kyang gus par byas nas 'chang bar gyur na /
T02TD2691E:219b-1: gza' dang rgyu skar ngan ba yang zlogs te /
T02TD2691E:219b-2: de rnams kyis srung pa dang skyob par byed do //
T02TD2691E:219b-3: tshe phyi ma la yang gza' dang rgyu skar bzang po las skyes nas /
T02TD2691E:219b-5: sba ba dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-6: snga ma bzhin du shes par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:219b-7: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo las /
T02TD2691E:219b-8: gza' dang rgyu skar gyi gnas skabs te bco brgyad pa'o /
T02TD2691E:219b-10: // / kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-11: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2691E:219b-12: gling chen po bzhi'i 'jig rten gyi khams yan chad /
T02TD2691E:219b-13: man chad kyi lha rnams kyi ming zung shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-14: gling bzhin gnas pa'i lha dang /
T02TD2691E:219b-16: gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi'i lha'o //
T02TD2691E:219b-17: de rnams kyi mchan nyid ni 'di lta ste zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-23: 'di lta ste ni 'di rnams lta ba'o //
T02TD2691E:219b-24: rgyal chen bzhi'i lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-25: rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i lha rnams kyi lus tshad ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-26: rgyang grags kyi bzhi cha gcig go //
T02TD2691E:219b-27: tshe tshad ni mi lo lnga bcu la /
T02TD2691E:219b-28: rgyal chen bzhi pa'i lha rnams kyi zhag gcig / nyin zhag gsum cu la zla ba gcig / zla ba bcu gnyis la lo gcig / rgyal chen bzhi pa'i lha rnams kyi tshe tshad mtha' ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-29: lo de ltar brtsis pa'i lha'i lo lnga brgya ste /
T02TD2691E:219b-31: mi ltar brtsis na lo sa ya phrag dgu yod do //
T02TD2691E:219b-32: nyon mongs pa ni dbang po gnyis sbyor bas tshim pa'o //
T02TD2691E:219b-33: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-34: lus tshad ni rgyang grags phyed do //
T02TD2691E:219b-35: tshe tshad ni mi rnams kyi lo brgya la /
T02TD2691E:219b-36: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams gyi zhag gcig go //
T02TD2691E:219b-37: de sum cu la zla ba gcig go //
T02TD2691E:219b-38: zla ba bcu gnyis la lo gcig / sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams kyi tshe tshad kyi mtha' ni /
T02TD2691E:219b-40: mi lo ltar brtsis pa'i bye ba phrag 'bum phrag bcu gnyis dang bye ba phrag dgu khri drug stong yod do //
T02TD2691E:219b-41: bar ma dor 'chi ba ni yod do //
T02TD2691E:220a-0: @220a * // 'thab bral gyi lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:220a-1: lus tshad ni rgyang grags bzhi cha gsum mo //
T02TD2691E:220a-2: tshe tshad ni mi lo nyis brgya la 'thab bral gyi lha rnams kyi zhag gcig go //
T02TD2691E:220a-3: de sum cu la zla ba gcig zla ba bcu gnyis la lo gcig ste /
T02TD2691E:220a-4: 'thab bral gyi lha rnams kyi tshe tshad kyi mtha' ni /
T02TD2691E:220a-5: lo de lta bur brtsis pa'i lo nyis stong thub po //

T02TD2691E:220a-8: nyon mongs pa ni 'khyud pa tsam gyis zhi ba'o //
T02TD2691E:220a-9: dga' ldan gyi lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:220a-10: lus kyi tshad ni rgyang grags gcig go //
T02TD2691E:220a-11: tshe tshad ni mi lo bzhi brgya la /

T02TD2691E:220a-13: de sum cu la zla ba gcig go //
T02TD2691E:220a-14: zla ba bcu gnyis la lo gcig go //
T02TD2691E:220a-15: dga' ldan gyi lha rnams kyi tshe tshad kyi mtha' ni /
T02TD2691E:220a-16: de ltar brtsis pa'i lo bzhi stong thub po //
T02TD2691E:220a-17: mi lo ltar brtsis na bye ba phrag lnga bcu rtsa bdun dang /
T02TD2691E:220a-18: lo sa ya phrag drug yod do //
T02TD2691E:220a-19: nyon mongs pa ni lag pa nas bzung ba tsam gyis tshim mo //
T02TD2691E:220a-20: 'phrul dga'i lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:220a-21: lus tshad ni rgyang grags gcig dang /

T02TD2691E:220a-24: 'phrul dga'i nyin zhag gcig / nyin zhag sum cu la zla ba gcig / zla ba bcu gnyis la lo gcig / de ltar brtsis pa'i 'phrul dga'i lha rnams kyi tshe tshad kyi mtha' ni /
T02TD2691E:220a-27: bye ba phrag nyis brgya sum cu dang /
T02TD2691E:220a-28: lo sa ya phrag bzhi thub bo //
T02TD2691E:220a-29: nyon mongs pa ni bgad pa tsam gyis tshim mo //
T02TD2691E:220a-30: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:220a-31: lus tshad ni rgyang grags phyed dang gnyis //
T02TD2691E:220a-32: tshe tshad ni mi rnams kyi lo stong drug brgya la /
T02TD2691E:220a-33: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha rnams kyi zhag gcig go ;
T02TD2691E:220a-34: / nyin zhag sum cu la zla ba gcig / zla ba bcu gnyis la lo gcig / gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi tshe'i mtha' ni /

T02TD2691E:223a-15: pang bar rdzus te skye ba'o //
T02TD2691E:223a-16: lha'am lha'i bu mo rnams ni /

T02TD2691E:223a-27: lha'am lha'i bu mo'i phrag pa'am bang bar rdzus te skye'o //

T02TD2691E:223a-43: lha de rnams kyi rang rang gi bsod nams kyi longs spyod che chung dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:223a-44: dbang che zhing 'khor mang po zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:223b-0: @223b lha de rnams kyang bsod nams kyi dbang gis 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:223b-1: de bzhin du dbang che ba'o //
T02TD2691E:223b-2: lha dang lha ma yin rnams gnas pa'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:223b-3: lha ma yin ni zhe sdang dang /
T02TD2691E:223b-4: ser sna'i dbang gis lha ma yin du grags te /
T02TD2691E:223b-5: de med pa ni lha yin no //
T02TD2691E:223b-6: de bzhin du yon tan dang ldan pa'i lha dang lha ma yin rnams gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:223b-7: de rnams kyis kyang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis bdag la srung ba gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:223b-8: thugs rje che zhing 'jig rten gyi khams la khyab pa /
T02TD2691E:223b-9: ma lus par rdzogs pa'i sems can gyi don la srung ba dang skyob par byed do //
T02TD2691E:223b-10: de lta bu'i rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gang zag gang gis kyang gus shing rjes su yi rang nas /
T02TD2691E:223b-11: lha de rnams kyis srung ba dang skyob par byed par 'gyur te tshe phyi ma la yang srung ba'o //
T02TD2691E:223b-12: sba ba dang zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
T02TD2691E:223b-13: sngar gor du bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //

T02TD2691E:234a-25: bu ram ka ra 'o ma dang //
T02TD2691E:234a-26: de rnams kyis ni dgang bar bya //

T02TD2691E:234a-28: gser dang dngul ni gzhug par bya //

T02TD2691E:234a-45: bum pa la ni yang dag brgyan //
T02TD2691E:234a-46: rdo rje slob dpon yang dag gis //

T02TD2691E:234b-0: tshul khrims @234b yang dag srung byed pa //

T02TD2691E:234b-6: de bzhin rdo rje slob dpon gyis //

T02TD2691E:234b-8: rdo rje slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid brtag pa'o //
T02TD2691E:234b-9: ras sam dar ram skud pa ni //
T02TD2691E:234b-10: rgyal po bu mo rje'u rigs ni //

T02TD2691E:234b-15: aom badzra s'u tra h'um phat ces bya bar byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:234b-16: slob dpon shar blta slob ma nub //
T02TD2691E:234b-17: de bzhin slob dpon byang du ste /
T02TD2691E:234b-18: slob ma lho phyogs blta ba ste //
T02TD2691E:234b-19: rim bzhin shar lho nub byang dang //
T02TD2691E:234b-20: byang shar mtshams dang lho nub dang //

T02TD2691E:234b-27: dbus kyi cha chen dang po la //

T02TD2691E:234b-29: gnyis pa'i cha ni padmar grags //

T02TD2691E:234b-35: de phyir phyed na cha yod pa //

T02TD2691E:234b-37: cha chen lnga po snang ba ni //
T02TD2691E:234b-38: nang gi lha rnams yang dag yin //

T02TD2691E:234b-46: phyi yi lha rnams yin pa la //
T02TD2691E:234b-47: de phyir cha chen phyed dang gsum //
T02TD2691E:234b-48: phyi yi sgor ni yang dag grags //
T02TD2691E:234b-49: de phyir phyed dang gnyis yod pa //

T02TD2691E:234b-56: sum cha gcig ni nang gi cha //
T02TD2691E:234b-57: sum cha gnyis ni ka bar shes //

T02TD2691E:234b-59: da ru ska dang gsum po ni //
T02TD2691E:234b-60: cha chung gsum ni mnyam par bya //
T02TD2691E:235a-2: de gnyis cha ni mnyam pa'o //
T02TD2691E:235a-3: cha ni sum cha gnyis gnyis te //
T02TD2691E:235a-4: nang dang phyi dang sgo ru yang //

T02TD2691E:235a-8: gser dang padma r'a ga dang //
T02TD2691E:235a-9: de bzhin aindra n'i la dang //
T02TD2691E:235a-10: de bzhin rigs lnga'i ngo bo 'di //

T02TD2691E:235a-12: rig sngags snying po rigs lnga'am //
T02TD2691E:235a-13: de yi sngags kyis byin rlabs bya //
T02TD2691E:235a-15: aom ma h'a m'a y'u r'i ye h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD2691E:235a-16: des mtshon cha rnams byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
T02TD2691E:235a-18: zla ba'i gdan ni shes par bya //
T02TD2691E:235a-19: de steng rin chen de bzhin rigs //
T02TD2691E:235a-20: rig sngags rma bya der gnas pa //

T02TD2691E:235a-24: ser po de ni byang na gnas //

T02TD2691E:235a-26: shar lho dang ni nub byang dang //

T02TD2691E:235a-31: rin chen padma rigs dang ni //
T02TD2691E:235a-32: de bzhin rin chen las kyi rigs //
T02TD2691E:235a-33: shar phyogs rim pa de bzhin du //

T02TD2691E:235a-36: mar me dang ni bzhi po dang //

T02TD2691E:235a-38: phyi rim mu khyud ra ba la //

T02TD2691E:235a-42: zur gyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhi ni /

T02TD2691E:235a-48: 'khor lo'i rtsibs la dgod par bya //
T02TD2691E:235a-49: de phyir lha rnams grub bzhi ni //
T02TD2691E:235a-50: kha dog dmar pos rnam par brgyan //
T02TD2691E:235a-51: lha rnams zur bzhir gnas pa ni //

T02TD2691E:235a-57: de bzhin ai ndra n'i lar shes par bya //
T02TD2691E:235a-58: lha rnams sgo dang bzhi po la //
T02TD2691E:235b-0: rgyu skar rim bzhin shes @235b bar bya //

T02TD2691E:235b-3: panytsa r'a ga lnga po la //
T02TD2691E:235b-4: dkar dang nag dang ser dang ni //
T02TD2691E:235b-5: dmar dang ljang gu lnga snang ba //

T02TD2691E:235b-20: gzhal yas khang gi steng na gnas //

T02TD2691E:236b-0: spu zing zhes bya ba'i rigs pa @236b ni ;

T02TD2691E:236b-36: dgra bo sdang ba rnams 'joms te /

T02TD2691E:236b-40: de'i yon tan gyi nus pas /

T02TD2691E:237a-2: yang na 'di'i zil gyis thams cad gnon pa'o //
T02TD2691E:237a-3: 'jigs pa thams cad las thar bar 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni /

T02TD2691E:237a-29: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:237a-30: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di ni /

T02TD2691E:237a-42: char dkon na ni 'bebs so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:237b-0: de na gnas @237b pa'i klu rnams ni dga' bar 'gyur ba'i phyir na /
T02TD2691E:237b-1: dus dus su char 'bebs shing dus dus su lo tog smin pa /

T02TD2691E:237b-3: de ba sa [*bas?] na rigs kyi bu 'am rigs kyi bu mo de'i bsam pa ji srid par char 'bebs par 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:237b-4: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo 'di'i gzi brjid kyis /

T02TD2691E:237b-9: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:237b-10: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'o //

T02TD2691E:238b-35: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo las /

T02TD2691E:240a-20: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240a-21: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240a-22: 'di ltar rgya mtsho chen po bzhi ni skam yang srid ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240a-23: rgya mtsho ni thar pa med cing rgya che ba ste /
T02TD2691E:240a-24: de yang me bdun gyi dus su bskams te /
T02TD2691E:240a-25: de yang rtag pa med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240a-26: sa ni nam mkha' la 'phar yang srid ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240a-27: bskal pa chen po'i dus su bskal pa'i mes sa rnams bsreg pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240a-28: zla ba dang nyi ma ni sa la lhung yang srid ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240a-29: da ltar nyi ma dang zla ba snang bar 'gyur te /
T02TD2691E:240a-30: de'i dus su yang nyi ma dang zla ba gnyis mes bsregs nas /
T02TD2691E:240a-31: nyi zla gnyis mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2691E:240a-32: klung ni rgyun nas ldog kyang srid kyi zhes bya ba ni rkyen gyi rang bzhin gyis klung de yang med par 'gyur te /
T02TD2691E:240a-33: de bzhin du sa dang rlung dang me dang chu la sogs pa /
T02TD2691E:240a-34: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi snang ba 'di yang med pa ste /
T02TD2691E:240a-35: sgyu ma dang rmi lam lta bu'i rang bzhin no //
T02TD2691E:240a-36: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' ni gzhan du 'gyur mis rid do zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240a-37: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240a-38: ma 'ongs pa rnams kyang de bzhin te /
T02TD2691E:240b-0: da ltar sh'akya seng ges bstan @240b ba'i bden pa 'di bstan pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-1: de nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-2: bden pa'i tshig gi de nas so //
T02TD2691E:240b-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-4: bcom ldan 'das kyis yang nas yang du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-5: kun dga' bo de lta bas na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-6: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo'i yon tan ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-7: bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod du med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-8: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di la zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-9: thugs rje che zhing sems can rnams kyi don byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-10: 'khor bzhi po zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-11: nye ba'i 'khor dang nang gi 'khor dang phyi'i 'khor rnams so //
T02TD2691E:240b-12: nye ba'i 'khor ni byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-13: nang gi 'khor ni nyan thos dgra bcom pa nyis brgya lnga bcu /
T02TD2691E:240b-14: de la sogs pa dge slong ngam /
T02TD2691E:240b-18: phyi'i 'khor ni lha dang mi la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-19: dge slong ma zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-20: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'dis srung ba dang skyob par byed pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-21: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos bcom ldan 'das la legs so zhes gsol te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-23: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pas /
T02TD2691E:240b-24: mgu nas legs so zhes zhu ba phul ba'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-25: bcom ldan 'das kyi ltar mnyan nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-26: sdud ba po kun dga' bo 'khor bzhi la bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-27: 'khor bzhi po zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-28: byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje snying po la sogs pa /
T02TD2691E:240b-29: bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-30: sh'a ri'i bu la sogs pa nyan thos nyis brgya lnga bcu'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-31: dge slong dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-32: dge slong sa ri la sogs pa /
T02TD2691E:240b-33: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba'i dge slong tsam mo //
T02TD2691E:240b-34: dge slong ma dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-35: sgra gcan 'dzin gyi ma sh'akya 'dzin la sogs pa brgya bco brgyad dang ngo //
T02TD2691E:240b-36: dge bsnyen dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:240b-37: tshong dpon mgon med la sogs pa dge bsnyen mang po'o //
T02TD2691E:240b-38: dge bsnyen ma rnams kyis rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo 'di la gus par byas so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:241a-0: de bzhin du de'i yon tan gyis sems can thams cad ni sdug bsngal thams cad bral zhing bde @241a * //
T02TD2691E:241a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:241a-3: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i chos kun dga' bo la gtad do zhe bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:241a-4: tshe dang ldan ba kun dga' bo dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2691E:241a-5: kun dga' bo la sogs pa nyan thos nyis brgya lnga bcu'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-6: tshe dang ldan pas ri dang zhes bya ba ni de bzhin nyan thos la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-7: lha dang zhes bya ba ni lha'i dbang po la sogs pa gzugs khams dang 'dod pa'i khams kyi lha rnams du ma 'dus pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-8: mi dang zhes bya ba ni mi'i rgyal po ma skyes dgra la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-9: du ma gnas pa'i lha ma yin dang zhes bya ba ni lha ma yin gyi rgyal po thags bzangs ris la sogs pa grangs med par gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-10: rlung lha dang zhes bya ba ni rlung lha'i rgyal po grangs 'dzin la sogs pa grangs med pa du ma gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-11: nam mkha' lding dang zhes bya ba ni nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po gser mig can la sogs pa nam mkha' lding grangs med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-12: dri za dang zhes bya ba ni dri za'i rgyal po zur phud lnga pa la sogs pa grangs med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-13: mi 'am ci dang zhes bya ba ni mi 'am ci'i rgyal po ljon pa la sogs pa grangs med pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-14: lto 'phye chen po dang zhes bya ba ni lto 'phye'i rgyal po yon tan grags la sogs pa du mar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-15: gnod sbyin dang zhes bya ba ni gnod sbyin gyi rgyal po ku be ra la sogs pa mang por gnas pa'o ;
T02TD2691E:241a-16: / srin po dang zhes bya ba ni srin po'i rgyal po 'jigs pa la sogs pa mang por gnas pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-17: mi dang mi ma yin pa gang dag 'khor der 'dus te 'khod pa de dag thams cad yi rangs te zhes bya ba ni rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na /
T02TD2691E:241a-18: de dag thams cad bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar gnas te /
T02TD2691E:241a-19: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo la gus par rjes su yi rang ba'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do zhes bya ba ni chos 'di bsam gyis mi khyab pa de dag thams cad kyi drung du /
T02TD2691E:241a-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis bden par bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2691E:241a-22: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo las rjes su yi rang ba'i gnas skabs te nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa'o /
T02TD2691E:241a-24: // / rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo las brtag pa lnga pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2691E:241a-26: // / rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo'i 'bum 'grel /
T02TD2691E:241a-27: rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po las kyi rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2691E:241a-29: // / pandi ta mkhas pa chen po aa mo gha badzras rang 'gyur du mdzad pa'o /
